wei shen me bu neng jin wu chen
ran hou an wei xin hong bao
ni dui shei hao wo zhen de
gang gang shi chi bao le ni
mei zi yao bu yao lai yi tiao
wo xian zai yue di di zai qing
hao xiang zhui ju a xian zai
wei xin ti shi yin wen jian jia zai na li
wo men dao di zai qi dai shen me
wo jiu ba mai de dong xi
jin tian mei you xi hao kan
xian zai wo jiu shi ruan xia lai a
nei ge jiu dian ni fang bian bang wo qu ding ma
wo xiang kan ni gen ni nan peng you qin zui
dan shi zhen de bu fang bian ya
yin wei jue de da jia you mi mi
bu xiang du da xue le me
jiang jiu shi kao wan le ge
ran hou suan qian ye shi ni suan
ran hou suan qian ye shi ni suan
ran hou suan qian ye shi ni suan
wo ye you hen qin lao de shi hou
qiang ge qiang ge ni nei er you
zhei ge shi pen shui xi you de
mei ci dou shuo wo shi pi hai
ta shi han guo jin kou de yo
shei jiang ni mei you ma wo e
ya jin de shi ni gen fang dong shang liang hao
you zhei yang de tang jie wo hen lei
ha ha ha nei ni hai chu lai
lao gong wo ye ai ni a
lao gong wo zuo jia wu xian a
nei ge nu: de you mei you huan
fang gong de shi hou ji de xian qu chong liang
ni bu teng wo wo jiu bu yao ni le a
ni de hu kou shi zai na li de
zhei ge wo dou hai mei yong
deng xia lei le wo jiu qu shui
ni de ye ji ta jian xia
lao gong zi wo qi lai le
wei sha hao ren jiu shi nei me duan ming
mei hao de ri zi zong shi liu ji hui yi
ni zhi dao tai zi zai na
ni yao qu kan dian ying e
wo hui xuan zui bian yi de
wo wan shang ji ni shuo a
ke shi wo zhi zhu zhong zhei ke a
zhong er shao nu: shi shen me gui

zhei ji zhang tu hao mo xing
deng jian ju di wen ni bian ge
dao shi hou bu yao han lei a
qi fu ni he zuo lei feng
ben da shuai de xin li hua
er qie hen da yi gu kou shui wei
wo yao qu shua ya zhun bei shui jue le
deng lao gong chi fan wen de lao po
xia ci wo men yi qi qu ma liu jia wan
bu dong you mei you shu ren kan dao

de rang ni lao ma zhi dao you wo zhei hao

pei ni du guo man zhang sui yue
wo jue de wo ru guo mei

ni de shen gao shi duo shao

wo dui ni jiu shi zhen ai bu zhi xian zai
ye shi ke lian wo de ba ba

bu shi ben lai jiu mei you

ni xi zhi ai shang qing di

jiu ma wo men zhei er chun gao
wo jia ma ma kao rou rou ji wo chi na

ni gang gang bu shi yi zhi
zhei tao biao qing zen me yang

an pai qu kai chu
zhe jiu shi wo suo hai pa de wo zheng zai bei gun xue qiu
gun xue qiu de xi sheng
jiu shi yi ge ming zi bei ti le jiu hui fan fu bei ti
bu jiu suo you ren du hui ti
ran hou suo you de shi du xiang xue qiu yue gun yue da
zui hou xue qiu hui ju cheng yi chang xue beng
wo jiu bei bie ren de xue huo mai le
hai bu shi chun bai de xue

wo yi ding gei ta men shuo ming bai le wo shuo ming bai le ma
ni kai chu nv shi
de xing wei bu jiu shi zai xiang ta gun xue qiu ma
bu nei shi zai zang
zai yi ci dao qian
nin bing mei you xiang wo ti wen
zai zang he gun xue qiu xiao ying liang zhe you shi yao qu bie ma
zai zang yu wo wu guan zhe jiu shi qu bie
nei bu shi wo de cuo wo de zhong dian shi zhe ge
wo xiang shuo wo shen bian zuo de jiu shi yi wei jing xuan jing li
wei shi yao xie lu de shu ju

ni shi de jing xuan jing li shi ba

ran er ni dang shi yi jing yi shi dao le shi tai de fa zhan
que xuan ze jian kou bu yan
nei ge shi hou zai biao mian shang hai kan bu chu shi yao duan ni
ke yi xiang nin bao zheng
you hen duo shi qing zheng zai an di li fa sheng

ni mei kan guo suan le
jiu shi nei ge tuo wo he xia shui de ren
ta shi ge ti bao nan dui dan ta ye shi ge huai ren
xian sheng you xie ren
xian zai ren wei ni shi zheng ge shi jian de he xin ren wu
suo yi wo xiang zhi dao ni shi fou neng miao shu yi xia
ni de gong zuo zhi ze
xian sheng you shi yao wen ti ma
zui chu wo bei chuan huan guo guo lai zhi shuo shi yi ge xiao xing ting zheng hui
wo fang qi xing zheng huo mian quan jiu lai le
er xian zai zhe li jiu xiang zhou jie lun yan chang hui xian chang
hao le wo men zheng zai diao cha ni de wan hu zhi shou
kan ni shi bu shi fan le zui xu yao xing shi diao cha
ni xu yao lv xing ni de xing zheng huo mian quan yao
e ha ta shuo bu suo yi
ni he guan xi bu cuo
shi wo he ta guan xi bu cuo
zai di yi jia ting ti an tou piao de nei tian
you ren kan dao ni he ta hai you zai yi qi
bu shi wo de peng you
ta zhi shi wo de tong shi
wo bu zhi dao wei shi yao wo gang gang shuo wo lia shi peng you
you xie ren ceng jing shi peng you er xian zai bu zai shi peng you
zi wo zhong xue nian dai qi jiu shi zhe yang le
ni zheng hao rang wo bu qia dang de shi hou shuo lou le zui
ni he xian sheng bao chi ju li ke neng shi ming zhi de
nei ni zen yang miao shu
ni he zong tong zhi jian de gong zuo guan xi
e fei chang qin mi
wo jing chang ba zi ji dang zuo shi yi ge xin xi qu dao
wo shou ji hen duo zhong yao xin xi
bing qie zhi jie jiang xin xi chuan song gei zong tong
zong tong nv shi wo xiang que ren ni shi fou yi jing fang qi le ni de zong tong xing zheng te quan
wo ke yi gao su ni
sui ran ci ci diao cha zhong bu xu yao ren he te quan
dan wo hen gao xing wo neng gou xie zhu diao cha
tan tan ni zai jing xuan cai liao zhong shi yong xie lu de lian bang shu ju de shi ma
ni gang gang cai shuo ni yao jin li xie zhu diao cha
dui wo de que shuo le
zong tong zhi dao you shuo
rang jia ting di yi ti an bu tong guo de shi qing ma

shang wu yi ling si san
ni luo hou gua fu xie er man er ling ge dian
wo men de rang ni yuan li ren lei
zai ni zhou wei zhuang dian xie shu rang ni kan shang qu geng xiang ren de chi cun
zhong hui ni nei sha lao mu jian ni de zi ran qi xi di ba
ni ge ti le mao de sha ye ren
dan hao xiao xi shi
jin fa niu shi yao qing kuang
you fen ta gei kou ma
jin nian ting nan ao de
geng nian qi bu tai hao dui fu
bai de a ni ye geng nian qi
bu ke neng ni jue dui geng nian qi
bu ni bi wo da suo yi wo
qi shi wo bi ni xiao liang sui
wo de yi ma hai an shi bai fang
dan wo de guan jie que shi you dian fu zhong le
wo men hai shi hui dao zhong guo de hua ti shang ba
shang wu yi ling wu ling
zhong guo ren ke neng yao gai yi xia tan hao de tiao jian
dan ru guo ta men zhen zhe yao zuo
ni yao zhun bei hao yan sheng qi li xi
rang ta men xiang xin ni bu hui zai xie shang le
ru guo he yi de tiao kuan bu jin ru ren yi
ni jiu shuo zhe xie tiao kuan wo men bu jie shou
ran hou ni tan kai shou zhang zhe yang
shi jing pai zhuo zi
ran hou you ge ren xu yao shuo yi ju zhe shi shi wu qian li de
cao zuo qi lai bi ting qi lai nan duo
wo men bu jie shou
ran hou wo zou chu qu
tai jia le zai lai yi bian
wo men wu fa jie shou
hai shi yi yang zhi shi xiang le dian
ta cong lai mei zhe yang guo
zhe ge bu cuo hen zhen shi a
a si peng xiao wu
shang wu yi yi si ba
bi jing xian zai wo men ti qian guo sheng dan jie qian ye wo song le ni yi dian dong xi
yi jiu ling qi nian di er ci hai ya hui yi shang shi yong guo de bi
wo xiang deng dao ni bei zheng shi dang xuan zhi hou
ni ke yi yong ta qian yi xie zhong yao de he ping xie yi
tai bang le kai se lin
zheng quan suo gei le wo yi zhang quan hei de jin shu xin qia
zhe zhen de biao xian le
wo men mu nv zhi jian wei da de qin qing a
ma qiao li kan kan wo gei ni le shi yao
ni gei ma qiao li zhun bei li wu le
ma qiao li xian zai ye shi wo men jia ting zhong de yi fen zi le ma shi ba ge men
wo ye gei ma qiao li le yi fen li wu dui ma gai li
qia zai nei le wo bu zhi dao zen yao hui shi
kan shi ben jiu shu
shi ge te lu de si tai yin shi ji de di yi ban
ta shi ma qiao li zui xi huan de shi ren le
ni zen yao zhi dao de ba ba
zhao ge te shu de di fang zhen cang zhe ben
wo zhu yi dao you liang liang zuo man ya zhou ren de gao er fu che kai guo lai le
chu fang gong zuo ren
qu zhao gei ma qiao li de li wu
wo hui xian jie shao yi xia dui fang
zhe wei shi lu qi jiang zhu xi
ta xue de shi hua xue gong cheng
zhe wei shi gong chan dang dang nei mi shu chang
shi zhong hua ren min gong he guo de zui gao ling dao zhe zhi yi
guo wu yuan zong li
ta er zi zai qiao zhi cheng da xue du da yi
zhe wei shi xiao jin dong di yi fu zong li
lun dun da xue jing ji xi
ta zui xi huan de ling shi shi dong cao mei gan
xie xie ni wo jiu ting jian le ge cao mei
zhe shi yi zhang zhong guo zui shou huan ying de qia tong ren wu
zuo cheng de jian tie ku ku zhu
zhe kan qi lai gen wo nv er kai se lin yi mo yi yang
ni nv er shi wei mei li de nv ren
er zhe shi yi zhi zhu a
xiang xin wo ru guo ni gen kai se lin ti hai yang shi jie
ni jiu hui dong de wo de yi si le
zhe jian zhi tai ke ai le tai gan xie ni men le
xian zai gai wo men de li wu le
zhe shi yi jian lai zi qing zhao de si chou pao
long de tu an yi wei zhao cai fu
ni men tai kang kai le wo you xie cheng huang cheng kong a
zhen de hai you a zhe yuan yuan chao chu wo men de xiang xiang a
ye chao chu wo men de zhun bei
zhe shi yi tiao lai zi qing zhao de gua tan
zhong jian de tu an mu dan
shi zhong cheng he pin de de xiang zheng
zhe jian zhi tai mei le er qie wo xi wang mei you bie de li wu le
xian zai lun dao wo men de li wu le
zhe shi ge mei guo shui jing dong
xiang zheng zhao wo men liang guo zhi jian
jian shi de you yi ji chu
ta de shan shuo ye ji tuo le
wo men dui liang guo dui hua chi xu shan guang de qi dai
xie xie ni men de shi tou
hai you zhe ping jiu
chan zi jia zhou na pa gu
hai you ling yi ping jiu ye chan zi yi ge ben di jiu zhuang
jiu zai xin xi lan
xin xi lan suan shi wo men de ben di
ta li ya zhou ye hen jin
suo yi ta ye suan ni men de ben di
wo men du shi lao xiang a
jiang a mei guo you yi ju lao hua
shao deng yi xia zhe hai mei wan
suo yi wo wei nin cheng shang zui hou yi jian li wu
yi gan chong man le li shi jia zhi yi yi zhong da de bi
shi yi jiu ling qi nian di er ci hai ya hui yi shang shi yong guo de bi
zhe shi fen shi fen he shi de li wu
le li shi jia zhi bing qie hen fu he wen
jin se dui zhong guo lai shuo shi hen ji xiang de yan se
le fan rong he hao
xian zai ta men zai tao lun
ni zen yao hui chuan de zhe yao sui bian
ta men shuo ni chuan de xiang ge fan ren
huo zhe xiang ge hai dao
hai xiang ben lian xi ce
wei shi yao geng nian qi nv wang mei you ti xing wo men
xia wu yi si wu
zhong guo ren zhun bei de li wu bi wo men duo zhe yao duo
wo men de qing bao xian shi ta men te hen ni
nv shi dan he ai mi de dian hua
qiao na gei zi ji bu le yi
wo tian ta you tong shi yao lou zi le
bu shi ta shi zhen de zhao zi ji jiao shang kai le yi qiang wo men zai ji zhen shi ni
kan zheng zai bo ni
wo cong qian ye shi zai zhe pian shu lin li he wo ji fu yi qi da xi
ta jiao hui le wo ru he zheng que
hou xuan ren rui an can zao bu xing
er nian ji de shi hou qiao na wan xiang pi jin ye she dao guo yan jing
xie er man hui ying rui an shi jian
guo qu he xian zai wo du shi zhe yao gao su ta de
qiang zhi hen wei xian
wo men qi dao ta zao ri kang fu
zhi shuo ba you duo zao
you yi xi lie fu za de gu zhe yi bu fen gu tou bei da lie le
shuo ta dui wo lai shuo you duo zao
dui qing kuang yan jun dan wo men hai bu zhi yu
wo ting bu xia qu le
xin han bu shi er shi ao bu lai en de le
de gan jin na dao zhong guo ren da ying de nei xie gong
lu zhu xi qing ni yi qi lu tian san bu
wo shi zong tong wo cai bu zou lu
ta ye shi zong tong ta xiang zou lu
de le xin zang bing yi hou jin xing xiu yang de di fang
ta xian zai hao dian le ma
zong tong ai sen ta qu shi ta si le ta zao yi bu zai le
yong lai chen lian san bu de
ni hai you kou xiang tang ma
neng ceng ni kuai kou xiang tang ma
wo ke yi he ni yi qi jiao kou xiang tang ma
xie xie zhong guo kou xiang tang a
ku a wo di yi ci chi
wa hao dai jing a
yi xiang bu dao a
wo you ge ruan jian
wo men xu yao he zuo xie shang
geng hao de chu li zhao xian wen ti
yin wei zhao xian ren min ye gen wo yi yang shi ren
chu le ta men mei fan chi
ma zong suan zhao dao ni le
shi xiang shuo qing chu wo he wo nv peng
bu zhi shi su shi zhu yi zhe wo men shi sheng su shi zhu yi zhe
ye jiu shi shuo bu chi rou dan nai
yi ji suo you zhu shu de dong xi
ma zao dian hui lai a
mo ni qia zai zuo rou kou huang dou zuo de huang you ni
bang ji le xie xie
qi jiang a nei shi wo nv er
xian ran ta mei ren chu lai nin shi shui
ta dui guo ji zheng zhi yi wu suo zhi
wo dai jia ren lai zhe zhi shi wei le dang yan hu
bie wo mei zhe yang wo mei nei yang
wo mei you wo mei zuo nei zhong biao qing
wo men jie zhao wang zhe bian zou ba
a si peng xiao wu
xia wu yi ling yi liu
xiao kai wo neng jie er ling ling da fu weng bi ma
da jia du xing zhao a
nei shi ni men cong an jian nei na de gei ma qiao li de li wu ma
nv shi nin zhen bu yong zhe yao ke qi de
tian ne tai liang yan le
zhe ge ma fu gu de
zhe si hua gan jue hao xiang shi yong
kai se lin rou shun de xiu fa feng zhi de lai mo mo
wo jiu jue de ni hui xi huan zhe zhong
xiang ta tou fa de dong
ma zhe mei de bu ke si yi a
ni zhi dao nei shi zheng fu cai chan ba
gang fan le lian bang zui
xin han bu shi er mou lv guan
shang wu qi ling san
zhe shi ni de shui yi
wo yi zhi gao chao de shi hou jiu xiang xiang zhe shen yi fu
zhu di xie er man sheng cheng yi xin yi yi wei le xin han bu shi er zhou
zhu di xie er man
zhen zheng de mu de shi shi yao
zhu di xie er man xiang qiang zou wo men de qiang
gao su zhu di xie er man wo men yao de shi zi you
ma de shi shi yao qing kuang
zhu di xie er man sheng cheng yi xin yi yi wei le xin han bu shi er zhou
guo jia bu qiang xie hui
quan guo bu qiang xie hui fa bu de
zhen shi sheng dan qi ji a
hao ba wo dai hui chu li zhe shi yi hui er jian
shang wu jiu san si
hao de ken te cai yi xia xin han bu shi er zhou you shi wo men de le shi bu shi
zong tong nv shi wo du bu xu yao yong wo cai zhe ge ci er le
he ai mi gan jin guo
ke ren zhun bei hao
wo zheng zai chu li xie shi qing
se lin nuo hai xu yao wo zai ti xing ni
zhong guo ren dui shou shi zhe shi er you duo min gan ma
ji ran zhe yang wei sha mei ci wo dian de hun tun tang song dao de shi hou du shi liang de
ming nuo wo zheng zai chu li yi ge guo ji jin ji shi jian
ke wei te de shi wo zhi neng shuo zhe yao duo le
zhe tai qi guai le
yin wei wo he a mi er a li a ba de
zai shang hu xiang guan zhu le
jiu zai wu fen zhong qian ta hai fa le yi zhang chi sha la de zhao pian ni
jiu fa sheng zai ta gang chi wan sha la nei hui
jian zou qu yi yang de jin ji shi jian
dui ke wei te lian luo chu de da shi
wo xian dai ta men qu zou
hao de xian zhe yang
suo yi xian zai wo men ai si bu qiang xie hui le
mei ye zong tong he a li a ba de shou xiang tong wan dian hua ma shang hui lai
ta zai nei bian gen ta nv er
zhong guo ren hen bu gao xing
shang wu yi ling yi qi
ta men geng gai le he yue de tiao kuan
bu zai fan dui zhong guo dui diao yu dao ti chu de zhu quan yao qiu
wei wan yi dian shuo
zhong fang dui jin qi fa sheng de shi jian gan dao fei chang fan nao
ni nv er de nei jian shi
nei wan quan shi ge wu xin zhi shi
kai se lin zhi shi yi shi mi shi
dan zuo wei ma ma que mei you zu zhi ta
wo yao zen yao zu zhi ta a wo zhi neng rang ta zuo wan a
ni ye shi ge mu qin ni you ge er zi
ni ken ding ye zhe yang zuo guo ba
zhe zhong shi zai bing dao ou er hui you
dan zai nei ye chun shu yi wai
wo qu ta men cong yi kai shi zhen zheng xiang yao de shi zhe ge
zhe xie dao ke bu shi tu ran chu xian de
shi shi shang zhe xie dao jiu shi tu ran chu xian de
zhong guo kao zai hai di chen ji wu shang da zhuang lai chuang zao dao yu
zong tong nv shi ni bu neng ge gei ta men zhe xie dao yu
zhe hui dong yao zheng ge di qu de
ma fan ni zai qu gen qi jiang tan tan
wo shi shi dan shi wo bu zhi dao
ta neng ting jin qu duo shao
dan shi ni yao zuo de jiu shi rang ta ting jin qu yi ge ci
ni zhi dao ma zhe
rang wo xiang qi le yin du he bu dan de tan pan
wo jiu zhi dao hui zhe yang
bu dan tai du qiang ying
wo de qu kan kan wo de ling yi ge wu ban le
mai dao zhe zhong chao hao chi de zhong guo kou xiang tang ma
ni gu ding kou xiang
yu zhong fang hui tan
xia wu si si qi
zhe ye gai bian bu le
wo men de ri ben peng you
zai diao yu dao ye you zhu quan de shi shi
lu zong tong jian chi ni fang
bu de dui ren he jiao yi chi you yi yi
wo men wu fa jie shou
lai mei xiang zhe yang
wo hui chong chu qu wo zhe jiu chong
mei men wu fa jie shou de
tan bai jiang ta cong lai mei zhe yang guo
wo bu zhi dao zhong wen zen yao shuo
wo zhi dao liang bai wan ting qi lai hao xiang hen duo bao bei er
dan qi shi bu duo zhe zhi shi wei zheng jiu
ba xi yu lin suo yao fu chu de xiao xiao dai jia
dan shi ni bu shi yao kan diao yu lin
lai jian du jia cun ma
zhe yang wo men jiu neng hao hao bao cun mei kan de la
zhe shi liang xing xun huan
ting qi lai hen you dao li ni
zai zhe er da lao yuan de gan ma ni
wo men deng hui zai tan ba
wo hui zai ni zhen tou shang fang xie xuan chuan ce de
ru guo ni xu yao qian fang mian de jian yi
ni lai zhao wo hao ma
wo shou xia ke you yi zheng ge cai zheng bu men ni
er qie ta men ni dong de
hao ba bu guan zen yao shuo ta men zhi qian ye hui huang guo
sui ran ni ba ba ai ni bao bei er
dan ta jiu shi ge pian zi
shi jue de wo ke yi
wo bu shi you yi yao da rao ni men de qin mi shi ke de
qu de le zhong da jin zhan
ni rang zhong fang ling dao zhen jiao da luan le
gao cuo a ma ma
wo gan jue ta jiu kuai yao dong yong
nei zhi di er ci hai ya hui yi de jin bi le ni
ni ma ma gei le zhong fang ling dao yi zhi chao bang de gang bi
dao ta zhi dao nei bi chang sha
ni jian zhi zao gao tou le
sheng ta de shi hou jiu yi jing xiang yi chang e meng le
shi ma wei shi yao
ni yin dao hen zhai ma
shi jin zai mei guo wo men shuo jin
zhong guo jing ji xian zhuang bi ren he ren xiang de du yao zao gao
zhe xie zhi cai zhen de zai xue ruo zhong guo de jing ji
er qie qi jiang zhe ge ren ta gao ao you gu zhi
wo ai huan le man ren jian
yin ci ru guo mei guo qu xiao dui zhong guo de zhi cai
bing you yi zai jie xia lai de er wu nian
yu qi zai gong ye jin shu fang mian de yao qiu da cheng yi zhi
zhong guo fang mian ye xu ke neng hui jiu xi cang wen ti jin xing xie shang
shang tao jie fang xi cang
bu bu ta men zhun bei kuang jia xie yi de xie shang
shi wei le tan suo min zu zi zhi de ke xing xing fang an
cheng wei jie fang xi cang de ren le
zhe ying gai gen zai xiang gang shi xing de yi guo liang zhi cha bu duo
yao cao fan zi ge er de mo jing le bao luo da wei xiu sen zheng zhi ge shou dai mo jing wei jing dian zao xing
zhe jian zhi shi ren lei deng shang yue qiu yi yang de li shi xing shi ke
wo de tian a wo sai lin nuo mei ye er jie fang xi cang de nv ren
bu bu shi du shuo le bu shi jie fang
nei e hai e zhou de gong chang zen yao ban
zai zui xin yi lun tou piao zhong qiao na du yao yao ling xian
qu ni mei de gong chang fan ren wo yao jie fang xi cang le
xian ran zhe dui yu
e hai e zhou he bei qia luo lai na zhou de shi ye zhe shi ge bu xing de xiao xi
ta men ying gai zi ji nu li shang da xue de
dan xin ni men fen lan zi ji de shi ye wen ti ba
fen lan bu cun zai shi ye wen ti
ge wei nei ge gai si de nuo bei er he ping jiang yao gui wo le
xi cang jiang hui ying lai zhan xin de wei lai
wei chao zuo de zen yao yang
mei ye er mei ye er sai lin nuo mei ye er
shuang bao tai wo de lao tian
bu wo ye shuang bei xing fu le
xin han bu shi er zhou te bie xuan ju
shang wu ba san yi
wo gai tou shui zhe ke jiao bu de
wo xi wang ta hui tou zi ji yi piao
bu hao yi si de zai gei wo zhang xuan piao
wo zhi shi wo zhi shi xu yao zai lai zhang xuan piao
wo bu xiang gen ni shuo hua
wo xiang gao su ni ge shi
dan zhe shi ji mi bu neng tou lu gei bie ren ming bai ma
ma ma yao jie fang xi cang le
kai se lin bai tuo xiao xin gan hai ji de ni xiao shi hou
ba jie fang xi cang de tie zhi
que nong bu xia lai le ma hai ji de ma
yin wei ba ta zhi jie tie zai qiang zhi shang le
hai xiao mao mi shi wo wo neng jin le ma
ni yi ge ren jin lai
xia wu yi er ling san
xian zai rang wo men gong tong qing zhu
chuan tong sheng dan wan yan
ji ju chuan tong wen hua di yun de
zi you yuan mu dan
wo men lai qie kai yi qi fen xiang ba
ni zhi dao wo men zhun bei hao le yao fa biao sheng ming
bu neng fa biao sheng ming
zhe xie yi ti du tai guo min gan
bu neng cang cu xing shi
dui de que ru ci
wo wan quan neng gou li jie
ran er ye xu xiang xi cang zhe yao zhong da de yi ti
yi bu xiao xin jiu bei mei ti zhi dao le
zhe yang yi lai quan qiu du hui zhi dao wo men de cheng jiu
ru guo tong shi you chuan yan zhi chu ni zai zhong guo hei ke gong ji mei guo wen ti shang
qi pian le quan guo ren min nei ke jiu fei chang bu xing le
zhe zhi ze tai huang miu le
wo men shou shang you ni de you jian zuo zheng
hao ba nei wo men deng ni men fa biao sheng ming
mai ke lin tuo ke xian sheng
ni de ling yang wen jian bei pi zhun le
nin he nin qi zi jiu hui ying lai yi ge zhong guo bao bei le
zai jian le an de lu
ru guo kai se lin you ren he guan yu ba xi tou zi de wen ti
shi ge zhen de zai ba xi de tou zi ma
wo bang ni na ba
ni zuo de zhe yi qie nv
hao le lu zhan yi hao yi ling fen zhong hou qi cheng
jin wan er ling gua fu xie er man ren shu le
wo cao qiao na ying le
bu guo hai shi ke yi shi wei tian qi de xiang rui
suo yi qiao na hui tou piao zhi chi wo er wo hui
xu gei ta da dian
guo hui yi yuan rui an
ni hao zong tong nv shi
wo gai jiao ni tong shi
wo zhi xi wang ni zhi dao wo
guo hui yi yuan qiao na rui an
hui qin zi tou gei ni ba ni
song shang zong tong bao zuo de yi piao
zhe dui wo yi yi zhong da
nv shi zheng hao wo men hai zai tong dian hua
xin han bu shi er zheng zai yu ya pian cheng yin de liu xing bing zuo dou zheng
de le wo bu hui
de ba nei ge fang wo bao
wo ke yi tui xuan xin han bu shi er de ren he ren
yi tui xuan ge mu si lin de ai zi bing
you shi yi lai zui xiao de zi sha bei xin li
ta ma de ai zi bing de kong bu fen zi
wo neng rang ta cheng wei xin han bu shi er de zhou chang
xing le jie fu ni he zui le
xin han bu shi er xin han bu shi er
wo de tian ne zhe shi wo de gong lao
wo men gang gang rang qiao na xuan shang guo hui le
kan kan zhou wei wo kan jian le hen duo shu xi de
zhi chi wo xiang xin wo de mian kong
ye kan jian le ji ge fan dui wo de
bi ru jie xi qia tang mu sen
hei jie xi qia wo kan jian ni le
que shi zi cong gao zhong zhi hou jiu mei jian guo ni le
wo xi huan ni de xin fa xing
ni xi huan wo de xin sheng huo ma
ji mi ou kang na wo deng le er ling nian xiang dui ni shuo zhe ju hua
wo de tian ne zhe du shi wo de cuo
ni gang gang rang qiao na xuan shang guo hui le
wo jue de ni cai shi ben dan
dan yi lu guo lai
you ge ren yi zhi xiang xin qiao na rui an
nei jiu shi qiao na rui an
zhe shi wo de meng xiang
ru guo ni zu gou xiang xin zi ji
zong you yi tian ni hui cheng wei guo hui yi yuan
xie xie ni xin han bu shi er xie xie ni
shi de wo men fei chang ji dong xie xie ni yi yuan xian sheng
qiao na hui he qi ta xin ren yi qi xuan shi jiu zhi
shun bian shuo yi ju wo yi jing jue ding
guan yu zong lv tan de hai bin bie shu
kai se lin ting zhao
wo yao ba ta dang zuo bei zheng jiu de jia chu de bi nan suo
wo ren wei zhe hen bang nv shi
ni yao ba wo fu qin de fang zi
bu hui zhi you shan yang de
wo shi shuo di fang zu gou
wo men ke yi shou na ge zhong bu tong de dong wu
ke yi you ya zi huo zhe
ye ke yi you ma
ye ke yi bang zhu kong
yi bang zhu da yang tuo ma
zong tong jing xuan bin xi fa ni ya
zhe tai bu ke si yi le zhen de shi
hai ni zen yao yang ni shi jian shen le yao
ni lia shi yao jie hun le yao
ni hai zhen shuo dui le
wo shi shuo zai xian ran ke yi jie shou fan wei nei de
shi dang de nei zhong ai hei hen gao xing jian dao ni
zong tong ken ding xi huan zhe xie tou tiao
huo li er ren zu
wo men you shi yi lai zui hao de zong tong
hao ba bie gei ta kan dao zhe tiao
bin xi fa ni ya wo zhen xi wang wo men ke yi bu yong zou
zhen shi bang dui bu dui
wo men hen kuai hai hui jian mian de
ru guo wo zai duo chi yi xie you zha dan gao
wo jiu bu neng zheng hao di chuan guo da ba de men le
zhe shi zhen hua zhe xie you zha dan gao hao ji le
wo men hen kuai hai hui jian mian de xie xie ni men
ni men jiu tao bu kai wo men le
zhe shi zhen hua yin wei ru guo wo men zai chi you zha dan gao nei wo men jiu hui bian de te bie pang
te bie pang xie xie
xie xie bie bie zai shuo le ting
bu wo shuo de shi you dian shi qing bu shi you wen ti
bu ta sheng qi le ta bu shi qi de jing shen shi chang le
duo hao de qun zhong dui yao
wo shi shuo ni zhen shi piao fang bao zheng a wo de peng you
zong tong nv shi wo shi lai wei ni fu wu de
ni shi tai yang wo shi mu xing de
wei xing shen zhi bu shi bi jiao hao de nei ji ge
niu yue shi bao guan yu de ren wu zhuan lan gang gang fa bu le
ting bu cuo de ying gai jiao zuo niu yue bao
guo qu de si nian rang yu xian shi shi jie jin jin xiang lian
xiang yi pi gu lang du xing shi jian
shen bian mei you ying sheng chong he ma pi jing
ni men zhi dao yao lang qi shi shi qun ju de dong wu
wo jue de wo geng xiang yi zhi gu du de song shu
ni lia du ying gai wei can jia zi xing che jian kang xiang mu er xuan liang zi xing che
shan di che gong lu che sui bian shi yao
qu wei li shi lai te xiong di
yong ta men de zi xing che wei xiu dian zhi zao le di yi jia fei ji
xie xie ni hui dian
you yi si de shi er wo men zai can jia jing xuan huo dong you bu shi kao bing yi mai
hei fa sheng shi yao le
zhe liang che shang you yi xing jian de jin zhang guan xi
ni zhi bu zhi dao guan yu nei ge gu du de song shu shi zen yao ping lun de
dao wo gang zuo xia lai de shi
ta shuang tui jin bing zhao zhao wo le ba
kan ba shi qing shi zhe yang wo cong lai mei you

nei da gai shi yi er nian
wo men yao zao yu da feng bao le fu ren
shi yi se lie hai shi zhong guo chu wen ti le
bu shi shi yi chang zhen zheng de ju feng
er qie ta hui cong hou fang qin xi bei qia luo lai na zhou
wo cai wo shi bi xu deng ju feng guo qu le cai neng qu nei er dui yao
fu ren wo men ke yi zai zhe li zhui zong feng bao wo you yi ge tian qi ying yong ruan jian
wo men you quan su yun zhuan de guo jia qi xiang fu wu xi tong
shi dan shi zhe ge ruan jian zhen de hen hao yong
wo men hui bao chi lian xi
zhuan xian bie li shen
wo xu yao ni qu fang hua gei geng duo de ping lun wen zhang
guan yu wo xuan ze de zhen shi yong yi
he shi ji de ling dao guan xi ke yi yao
wo yi zhi zai nu li zuo fu ren dan shi ta men du feng kuang mi lian
ren men xi huan tang mu dan shi wo ying gai huo de ken ding yin wei shi wo xuan le ta
wo xiang yao geng duo de tou tiao
kan kan zhe chang feng bao yao
zhe li hao an jing a
jiu xiang shi fang man tu shu guan li yuan shi ti de tai ping jian yi yang
wo qia hao xi huan an jing xian sheng
dang wo mang de shi hou ta neng rang wo hao hao zuo shi qing jiu xiang wo xian zai zhe yang
shi ha wo ting xiang da jia de shen zhi ye xiang
hao le gen ni shuo hua zhen shi fei jing
e lao tian zhe ge di fang zhen shi si qi chen chen
zi cong zou ren yi hou

ni zhi dao yao zhi yao dang wo

ni te yao gan peng wo de dan dan shi
yi ge xiao hua zai ren men

zong si ling ji zong tong

ni ying gai xie yi ge hui yi lu

bu wo bu hui shuo shi yi wei ming xing

wo ben lai yao tan tuo le
dan yi kan jian ta nei wu guan fen jia de lian
wo jiu ta ken ding ting bu jian wo men shuo hua shi ba
wo men ba yi zi zhuan yi ge jiao du ba
dao wo men ting de jian bu shi ma
de ta bing bu zhi
dao de yi tiao duan
ta sha du ting bu
kan jian mei ru guo feng suo hang ban kai shi shi shi
dui yu can yi yuan he ta de jing xuan huo ban er yan
zhe ge ken ding shi bu gong ping de
yin wei ta men hui bei kun zai fu luo li da
ta men bu xiang wo men yi yang ke yi qin fu zai hai xian chang wei wen
jiu rang ta men sui shao kao jiang zhi er qu ba
huai le zhe yi zi
zhou chang wo hen yi han gao su nin
wo men hui zai ni de ji chang jiang luo
jin guan ni fan dui wo men zhe yao zuo
ru guo ni neng gou fa chu jin ji yu jing de hua
wo xiang yi fen lai zi lian bang zi jin de mian bo zhi li ke yi cheng wei ni men de gan lu
hao de wo jue ding fa biao sheng ming chu yu jin ji yu bei zhuang tai
xie xie ni zhou chang
ya fang yi wan ge xin
dao ni shi shi yao ma
wo de ming zhi zhi xuan
hao ba rang wo men qu zhui zhu feng bao ba xiao biao za
zhe bu shi ju feng nei dao di te yao shi shi yao
wo de ying yong shang shuo shi he feng
zhe xie shu du mei you dao xia
wo bu xiang kan dao zhe xie yi li bu dao de shu
shuo wo de feng bao qu na er le
ni nei ge ying yong zen yao gao de
ni zui hao ba ni hua zai nei shang mian de qian tao hui lai
ta qi shi mian fei de
wo geng xin le ruan jian zhi hou ta jiu chu xian zai wo de ping mu shang le
ran hou wo jiu zhe shi ge sha jie zhao wo jiu yong le
suo yi zhe ge feng bao xian zai zai wang na er zou
hui qu pai she feng bao zhao pian ni shi zhe ge yi si yao
dang shi wo ti chu de shi hou zhe hai jue dui shi ge hao zhu yi
hao ba wo yan chi le yi dui hang ban
er qie hai ba zheng fu jiu zhu jin song qu le bie de zhou
wo zen yao bu ji de ni dang shi ti dao zhe ge ke neng xing ni
you shi hou ni xu yao du yi ba yun qi
bu xing de shi wo men de ma mei you ying
dui a ken ding mei ying
ta kua di yi ge lan de shi hou jiu ban dao le ran hou bei yi qiang bi le
ran hou xian zai yi qun fa guo zha zha ba ta sai jin fa shi chang gun le
ni yi hou bie gei wo na jing xuan
he wo de zong tong wei zhi du yun qi hao ma
cuo de tai duo shuo hua tai bu guo nao zi le wo dao
lai zi nei ge shi wu de dao le xiang he nin jian mian
zhe shi ge xiao hua yao
hua ni wei sha hui zai zhe er a
wo zai he dui ji gou de hui ying
hen duo gao ge zi nv ren du bei sao rao le
ran hou xian sheng ye shi qi zhong zhi yi
hao ba zhe shi yi ci jing xuan fang wen yao
shi de ni zai zhe li de shen fen shi hou xuan ren er bu shi zong tong
hao ba nei zhe xie ren zai zhe er gan sha de
jiao zhu jian zhu zhuang shi
nv shi wo men hai zu zhi le yi ge zhi dan gong chang qie zi de fang wen
wo zhi bao zhuang ji dan de yi ge gong chang bu shi nei ge da xing de zhi wu
wo men ben lai xi wang dai ni qu kan kan gong chang
dan shi wo men gong chang zai feng bao zhong shou dao le yi xie po huai
wo men ye hui xiang qu kan kan de zan men zou

wo men lai kan kan
 zhe ge wu ding shou dao le yi xie po huai

xie dou fu zha jian zhu er

ni zai zhe er de gong zuo shi shi yao

wo men yao rang ta liu yi dao wo men de jia zhi

mei you hu zhao ni mei ban fa li kai ye men
ru guo zhe shi zhen zhu de zhi yi
ni hen kuai jiu hui jian dao ni de di di
wo gao su guo zi ji zhi yao wo men cong jian yu chu qu
wo jiu yong bu zai ta jin ling yi zuo jian yu
zhe li mei you mai ke er si ke fei er de
zhe shi wei le yao wo de hu zhao er she de pian ju
ao ma shi wo zui xin ren de shou xia zhi yi
xin ren si hu zai zhe ge guo jia yi qian bu zhi
deng wo yi xia xing ma
wo hui xiang ge bian tong de ban fa
dui ba ta men fa gei ni de nei zhang
qia ni er wu ti si
dui qia ni er wu ti si ta zai zhe li ma
ta shuo dui tu pian zhong de nan ren jiu zai zhe li
wo men ke yi qu tan shi ta
dan jin jin shi yin wei wo men gen xi ba you jiao qing
ni wei shi yao shuo zhe ge ming zi
shi yin wei wo di di de wai tao
hai yi wei zai zhe jian shi shang ni men shi zhan zai zhen zhu zhe bian de
xi ba bu xi ba
qia ni er wu ti si shi ge chou ming zhao zhu de kong bu fen zi
ta yin wei mou sha bei zhua lai de
ta he kong bu zu zhi shi yi huo er de
qi tu dian fu zheng fu
bie zhe yao shuo chao piao ge
ni zhi dao nei jue bu shi mai ke er
wu lun ta shi he fang shen sheng
wo men du yao jian dao ta le
wo ba ba shi ge zen yang de ren
wo qin sheng ba ba
mai ke er si ke fei er de
jiu xiang yi chang feng bao
dai shang zhao xiang ji
wo xiang zheng ming ta hai huo zhao
ta yan zhi bao biao
ta hui cong zhan lan de tian kong zhong
xian shen yu ni de sheng ming li
lai wu ying qu wu zong
dan feng bao hai shi neng hui lai de
wen ti shi ru guo hui lai le
nei hui shi ren mian yi jiu ni
hai shi wu shi ren fei le ni
ni shuo de xin shi shi yao yi si
wo men hui ba ni jiu chu lai de
wo de ming zi bu jiao mai ke er
wo ye bu zhi dao ni men shi shui
mai ke er gen wo shuo hua a mai ke er
mai ke ni zai gan shi yao gai si de
hua sheng dun te qu
ju nei hua da piao xuan ren zheng hai you san tian
mai ke mai ke lin tuo ke ding de er ren zhuo
ke yi jiu zuo le
yi qie jiu xu dai ma que jin lai
wo neng zai shuo yi ci wo cuo le
wo you duo bu hao yi si ma
kan kan zhe zhen shi ta men zhen xi huan wo men shi ba
hai tai hao le ni shuo shi yao
wo bu shi nei zhong ai dao qian de ren
ke shi ni xian zai ting xi huan de shi ba
tai xi huan le xiang zai ting yi ge ma
zhen de zhen de dui bu
zong tong he bei er de xian sheng xiang shou le yi dun mei wei de wan can
chi le you dang di yu min pu zhuo dao de lan xie
yi ji yi dao nai lao jia yao hai gong yin le chan zi fo meng te zhou bi yu shan jiu zhuang de
mai ke ru guo zong tong he ta de xin nan you zheng ri xun huan zuo le
ta zen yao neng zhuan zhu yu jing ji shang ni
zong tong yi zhi du hen zhong shi cai zheng wen ti
jue bu hui xie dai ta zai jing ji wen ti shang de ze ren
zai ren fu zong tong shi ta jiu shi mei ye you zheng wei yuan hui zhu xi
ta de zheng ce shi de you zheng bu men de fu zhai
cong liu wu ling yi jian shao dao le liu er ling yi chu tou
nei hua da zhong ji piao shu
hao de xiong ying cheng yuan men deng hui er jian
hao le wo men jin zao you duo de le liu piao
yong yuan suo xiao bu le cha ju
bu guo hai you bu nei yao zao gao de yi mian
da zhong ke xi huan ni he cha li bei er de le
jiu lian hua er jie ye wei ni men bo qi le
shi chang hao zhuan le
dan zhe ge shi hou bu xia jiang dui wo men lai shuo jiu shi shang sheng le
zong tong nv shi shou dao xiao xi cheng zhong guo hei ke yi jing
ru qin le guo jia an quan ju de fu wu qi
wo you hao zhu yi wei shi yao wo men bu zhi jie gei zhong guo ren
yi ge ta men de deng lu zhang hao he mi ma ni
shi ba gei da jia du jie sheng bu shao shi jian
nv shi shi pin yao wu guan li ju zheng zai mi su li zhou
yi ge ji chang diao cha sha men shi jun de bao fa
hai you lai zi tong xun bu men de xiao xi
mei ti duo ci ti dao nin ming tian
he cha li bei er de zai niu yue de
guo jia li shi bo wu guan zhi lv
cha li shuo ao bu lai en mei you xiao mian bao zhan rou zhi
jiu bu hui gei ta lao po kou
ni neng jiao wo zen yao zai tui te shang zhao dao
ren men da tan te tan wo he cha li de tui wen ma
dang ran kan jian xia mian nei ge an niu le ma
ting zhao ren zheng jiu zai ming tian le
wo de yi si shi shuo zhen de wo men hai you shi yao li you
xiang xin wo men mei you xiang yi ge gao zhong can yi yuan xue sheng yi yang gao za le ma yi xiang te shu gei chu gao zhong sheng le jie zheng fu de xiang mu
qi shi nv shi bao qian
wo chi dao le wo hao xiang fa xian dian shi yao
nei hua da zhou de tou piao shu ju
xian shi biao zhun cha chao chu jun zhi ji bei
tian a ken te shuo neng ting dong de
wo jue de ken ding you shu ju
neng zheng ming zai nei hua da you lou piao
ni he cha li bei er de de zhao pian yao fa zai ming li chang shang
jia fei mao wo men xian zai zai tan lun
nei hua da de de shi hao ma
ken te ni neng gao su wo men shi yao
wo ye xu ke yi zhun que jie shi shuo ming tou piao yi chang de qing kuang
yao shi wo ke yi yong lan jie mo xing
fen jie hun za bian liang de hua
hao le suo yi wo men bi xu de tui chi
zhong xin ji piao ren zheng
wo jiu shi zhe yao xiang de nv shi
wo ke yi qing lv shi shen qing jin zhi ling
jiu rang wo jian jian ji mu hui te man de le
zai diao da ta zhi hou
ta jiu hui tong yi tui chi ren zheng le
ling hai shi diao chou
tian a ai mi shi ta men de hui mian ya
hao le de kai shi qu mei ti shui yu diao yu le
wo xiang rang ni an pai
wo he la si wei jia si gong bao de nei de mi xie er
yi ji lei nuo zhi xing de su shan bei li
ai mi an pai ba su shan bei li lei nuo zhi xing quan bu de
zong tong nv shi ni jue de shui zui shi he
zai hui yi shang zuo wo de zhu shou ni
wo xu yao he bao bo dan du tan yi xia
ni men xian chu qu ba
bao bo zai hua sheng dun te qu wo du kuai feng le
wo gan jue bei kun zhu le
you shi yao fang fa neng rang wo qu nei hua da ma
xian rang wo bang ni ying de zong tong zhi wei ba
ran hou ni jiu ke yi deng lu kong jun yi hao ling yu le
ru guo ni yuan yi de hua hai ke yi niao zai kai sa pen quan li
shao lai le bao bo wo zen yao ke neng xuan ze zhu kai sa jiu dian
nv shi zhong qing ju mei zhou jian bao
kan jian le ba luan qi ba zao de zhao huan
wo jiu shi shuo zhe xie deng hui er zai gen ni tan
kai se lin bie yong ren he bu ya de pian duan
ke quan du shi a lao ma
jiu shuo ji lu pian ma
mei ye zhong ji zong ban gong shi
nei hua da qia sen cheng
hou lai ye mei ni xiao xi
su fei gao su ni le
zhe ge tai miao le
dan suo fei bu zai
ni mai le diao zhi huan lai dian san zhuang bing cha
san wu zhi ke tang jiang
ni chuan lan bei xin ye man ke ai de
jin nian zhen shi dian er bei
nv shi fei chang bao qian de tong zhi nin
wo men zhua dao de nan xing bing bu shi a bu la du sa yi de
yi se lie nei bian zhi dao zhe shi ma
yin wei ta men shi yi qun bei bi wu chi de sha bi
bu hao yi si nv shi
jin wan ba dian ban xing ming shi mai ke mai ke lin tuo ke xie xie
bu hao yi si ken te gang shi yan yue ya xin kai de can guan
li hai a ni zen yao gao ding can wei yu yue de
su zong shi yong wo de ming zi ti zong tong yu yue
suo yi wo zi ji ding zhuo de shi hou du you hao wei zi
wo zhong xin kai shi chi fan le
yi sheng shuo nei ge qing chang mei you zao cheng yong jiu xing shang hai
zong tong zhang hu de tui te zhang hao hen huo yue
bu hui ba zhi you wo hui yong zhe ge fa tui a
ha ha ha zhen cha li bei er de xian zai ke lun dao ni le
zong tong shi zai fa tui te
bu hao yi si wo de wo xu yao jin qu yi xia
hen bao qian xian sheng wo bu neng rang ni jin qu
qiu ni le ma qiao li wo you hua gen zong tong shuo
wo men zhua dao de qi shi shi a bu la du fa yi de
shi ge dang di xue xiao de lao shi
nv shi yao shi ni ting dao de hua bu yao fa tui te
ni zhe shi zai gao shi yao yao e zi
jiu shi ni fa de guan yu ao bu lai en de tui te nei ge ying xiang tai bu hao le
wo zhi fa gei cha li le a
bu zhe shi gong kai de suo you ren zai tui te shang du neng kan dao
shi yao jiu shi xie wan xiao hua a wo gang zhi shi
shi dian le nei ge yu mao jian
wo zhi dao a ni zhe jiu shi fa le yi tiao tui wen
gai rui wo jiu shi an ni jiao wo de nei yao fa de a
dan wo bu shi nei yao jiao de a
ni jiu shi nei yao jiao de

rang wo gao su ni wo xiang rang ni gan ma
jiu gei wo dai zhao hao ma
zhe suan shi dui ni de cheng fa gun ba
nei wo qu pao dian cha
ni hai shi xie zhao ba
rui dian shou xiang gang cai
yong xiao zha le de biao qing zhuan le ni nei tiao tui wen
cao dan de wo men jie xia lai zen yao ban
wo men gan cui si bu cheng ren
fan zheng shou ji yi zhi du zao dao hei ke gong ji

zong tong nv shi ni que ding zhe shi ni ben ren fa de ma
ni shi yao yi si wo ben ren
dui a ye xu bai gong de dian nao xi tong
bing mei you wo men xiang xiang de nei yao an quan
ye xu bai gong fang huo qiang de lou dong
bi tao jin nv zi gong mao shang de dong du duo ni
wo tian wo zui tao yan zi gong mao le
xie shi you ge hei ke xi ji lai

zhe yang de hua ni de si xin bei gong kai

bu nv shi ni ya gen er bu zhi dao fa sheng le shi yao shi

xi mei zhan zheng hou zhe yi zhi shi

hei ke xi ji lai zi zhong guo da lu

zong tong fei chang zhen liang

zong tong xiang xin wang luo an quan gong zuo
dui mei guo de wei lai sheng cun zhi guan zhong yao

jing xu shi dai fa
nv zong tong gu ji yao deng dao er ling ling ling nian ba
de xian sheng bei er de xian sheng wo hen bao
wo zhi dao da jia du zai deng ta dan shi
ta gang cai fa duan xin lai shuo ta yao wan yi dian cai neng guo lai
ni que shi ta shi fa duan xin gao su ni de hai shi shuo ta yi jing fa tui zhao gao tian xia le

nei de mi xie er zai er ling ling liu nian jiu qu shi
la si wei jia si gong bao
er ling ling qi de shi hou ting kan
wo lian xi shang le lei nuo zhi xing de su shan bei li
lei nuo zhi xing bu shi yi fen bao zhi er shi yi jia he fa ji yuan
dan ta si hu hen kai xin neng gou
jin ta suo neng bang zhu wo men de jing xuan
tian na nv shi dui bu qi
ta kan qi lai gen yuan lai de bao bo mei sha liang yang a
nv shi jin tian zao shang ta gao su wo you tai ren dao zhi le ju feng
ta gang jin qu he hui te man hui mian le
ru guo ta yao zai zhuo zi la shi sha de zen yao ban
nv shi yi ta de nian ling lai shuo ru guo ta neng zai
zi ji xiang la shi de shi hou la shi de hua zhe jiu suan shi ge zhong da sheng li le
ai mi zhe ge hui yi jue dui bu neng
huo guo jiao ke shu cang ku da lou
kuai qu ben xian bie gua
xie shi qing yao gao su
bao bo zhi dao mei you zhong guo hei ke de shi le
wo ke neng gao su ta le
bie dan xin nv shi
wo men hui ba ta sai dao nei hua da qi fei de di yi jia fei ji shang
zai ba ta sui bian reng dao e ke la he ma de mou ge di fang
bu guan ta shi bu shi lao nian chi dai zheng wo cha le xia su shan bei li de tu pian
chang de shi ke yi yi cao a
ni hao wo shi dan qing liu yan
ma de di er jian shi
zai shuo ta yao jia ye ting he li de
wo shi li cha de shi pei lei ya yao wo xiang shuo
ni ying gai mei tian ya yao gei wo liu ge xiao xin xi ya yao ya
zai kai kuai dian yao
ru guo ni neng gei wo zu liang bo rui de hua ke yi
bie fei hua gan jin kai che
zan men xian zai jiu xiang nei ge zhu ming dian ying dao huo xian li mian yi yang
ni men kan guo ba luo bo te de ni luo he bu lun ni man nei yi mu
guang shi xiang xiang nei yi mu wo jiu hun shen qi ji pi ge da
zhe ta ma dao di shi yao qing kuang
hui te man xian sheng bu la de li xian sheng
yi ding ma shang jiu hui hui lai de
wo xian zai chu qu zou zou
kan kan bao bo shi bu shi hai xu yao shi yao dong xi
da jia wan shang hao zai wo men kai shi zhi qian
wo xiang xian zhi xie zhe ci wan yan de zhu ban ren
yi ji zhe ge te shu zu zhi chang qi de kang kai tou zi ren
cha er si bei er de er shi xian sheng
duo xie shi di fu wo xiang shuo da jia kai chi ba
dan shi wo de nv ban hai mei dao
zong tong du zhe yang dui ba
xi wang ta neng zai da jia lao cheng hua shi zhi qian jin kuai gan dao
wei shi yao xian zai suo you ren du bu jie dian hua
shao deng nv shi wo zai gei dan da ge shi shi
dan ni er duo guan jing yin le ma
wo du gei ni da le bai ba shi ge dian hua le
bao bo zou zhi qian
hui te man rang wo men ba shou ji du guan le
ni shi yao yi si hui yi jie shu le
hai mei ni dan zhe bu neng zu zhi wo men de xiong ying
fei dao jie shang bing zuo zhao chu zu che li kai a
na ba ta de zui bi
ru guo hui yi hai zai ji xu de hua shui he hui te man zai yi qi ni
wo bu shi zao gao su guo ni le ma
shi pei lei xian sheng bao bo bu la de li zai na
lao shi shuo wo ye zheng yao wen ni ni
ni neng gen wo pai zhang zhao yao
fang zai wo de bo ke xian tan shi pei lei er san shi shang
gao su xiong ying wo hen gao xing jian dao ta
ming tian wan shang liu dian
zhe ge zhou de mei yi zhang xuan piao du jiang bei ren zheng bing ji shu
bing bu shi mei yi zhang xuan piao xuan ju qu wei xiao zhi shi
cong li shi shang kan yi qi xuan piao shi ke guan cun zai de
you shi hou duo da yi liu de xuan piao hui bei nong diu huo reng diao
shi zhe ge hui de mu de
wo wei wa xiao xian de yi shi xuan piao gan dao bao qian
wo men dao chu du zhao le dan hai shi yi wu suo huo
suo yi shuo zhu ni men hao yun ba
ru guo ni zhen de peng qiao zhao dao le yi zhang xin xuan piao de hua
wo di ge shen ya
yao tao chu hua lai de
ai mi shuo wu ge ni zui xi huan de de ni luo de dian ying
chu le bai jian yue fu da ren
hao wu yi wen zhe shi zui hao de
ken te shi wa xiao xian bie wen wo zen yao zhi dao de
ken te rang si fa bu lai guan zhe shi ming bai yao
ba ni de shu ju du gei ta men bang ta men suo xiao fan wei
shuo wo de ji xu shu ju ju
jiu shi nei shu ju shi yao
ai mi hai shi mei you xiong ying de xiao xi yao
nan bu cheng ta kai zhao ge cao ji heng chuan mei guo yao
fu ren wo men xian zai po qie xu yao you ren zai fa ting shang
zhi shao tuo dao wo men zhao dao lou diao de xuan piao
wo kao lv guo le
ran hou shi nv guo lai
gen wo men shuo nv wang bi xia
qing ni men can guan ta de wang guan
neng xiang xiang yao yi ge a la ba ma zhou bo ming han de xiao nan hai
he ying guo nv wang
nv shi men xian sheng men rang wo men huan ying mei guo zong tong
xie xie kan kan ni
lan hui se de qun zi zhen hao kan a
ni hao a zai nei hua da zhuang tai hen hao a
nei xin zhen fen nei hua da a ni hao
ji xu he yi bei da jia kuai zuo xia ba
wo deng bu ji yao ting ting nei ge shi yao
jian long pi jia zhi shi zhe
wo cong che dui guo lai de lu shang ba kou hong nong diu le
dan xin wo zhe you yi
zhe zhi ni qu ba nei zhi zhao hui
cuo guo le shi yao
gai rui gang gang gei wo men jiang le jian ying guo nv wang de shi
ta jiu shi ge chou biao zi
nei hua da zui gao fa yuan
piao xuan ren zheng ting zheng hui
wo men hai mei zhao dao nei xie piao ni xu yao zai tuo yi hui
ai mi fa ting shen sheng bu ke qin fan
wo zuo bu dao shi yao tuo yan
zhe ge an zi jian dan de yi mu le ran
bu guo zhe ye rang ta ru ci fu za
ben ting jiang shen li mei ye yu nei hua da de an jian
guan yu yan qi zhong shu de ti yi
kai shi zhi qian qing yun xu wo dui ji ge guan jian ci jin xing ding yi
xuan piao yi zhang xuan piao shi shi yao ni
wo jue de da an xian er yi jian ba
nin que ding yao fa guan da ren
tou piao zhe ge ci zai bu tong wen hua bei jing zhong you zhao xu duo han yi
ke yi zhi qing dian
gou huo pang de tiao wu
huo zhe jing mo de dian tou
xian zai zai zhe ta de han yi shi shi yao
you ji ga mai ji de xiao xi yao
wo men xu yao zhao dao bao bo bi xu gan zai
kuai kan zhe ge ba ni pai de duo hao kan hai you zhe zhang
kuai na kai you nei ge nei da hua jing cha de xiao xi yao
shi yao xiao xi du mei
nin shuo shi yao ta lai na le
jian dao ni zhen shi tai bang le
jin tian you shi yao tang
ni xiang he shi yao yang de tang
nei jin tian xing qi ji le
nei jiu shi hai jun dou mei wei ji le
fu ren nin xu yao hei bao bo
wo shi bao bo bu la de li xian sheng jian dao ni hen gao xing
nei hua da de ji shi xin wen
gen ju xian bao mei guo si fa bu men ren yuan
zhao dao le shang xing qi zong tong da xuan shi
de yue yi wan feng mei you ji shu de tou piao
yu ci ren jia zhong
wu si sui de mei guo you ju zhi yuan wan si ao te luo
bei mei ye you zheng wei yuan hui guan bi ting ye hou
ao te luo bian de shi fen bu wen ding
hai shi ge you zhao gao du shi yong xing
tong ji xue jia zhi jing yan de xing zheng qu
ni shuo de wo yi ge zi ye mei ting dong
bu guo ni jiu ji xu zuo nei xie suan zhu de dong xi ken te
shui yong zhe shi qu xiao ni ye bu yong
hao ji le du ting wo shuo kai lun
bi xu rang zhe xie piao shu de dao cheng ren zuo de dao yao
ta hui de bu ran jiu huan ren
ai mi wo zhi dao zhe ji tian bu shi hen jin ru ren yi
wan quan zao tou le fu ren
wo xi wang ni ming bai
duo yu le li cha de wo cai neng jie jue zhe xie wen ti
yi ding yi ding yao zhuan da wo de gan ji
fu ren wo men zai zhong guo de da shi da lai de
kong pa zhong guo ren
kai shi hui ying nin zhi qian de zhi cai wei xie le
yi fen zhong de qing song du bu neng gei wo yao
wo wen wen nei xie zhong guo ren
fa guan da ren wo gang de dao xiao xi
zai wa xiao xian zhao dao le nei xie wei jing tong ji de tou piao biao
wo shen qing zhong xin tong ji piao shu
fa guan da ren fan dui
zhi dao wo men zhong xin shen li
ming zao shi dian zai ji xu
jing guo jin tian fa sheng yu nei hua da de zhen liang shi jian
zong tong yi jue ding pin qing xiong ying bao bo bu la de li
fan hui hua sheng dun dan ren ta xin de
wang luo an quan zhu guan li ji sheng xiao
tong shi guo wu yuan bao gao cheng
xuan bu le yi xi lie zhen dui mei guo de zheng ce
bao kuo mei guo chu kou zhong guo de xin xian zhi ling
dong jie zhong guo jing nei de mei guo tou zi ji jin
dui mei guo gong min ling yang wai ji er tong de jin ling
yi xie qi ta de zheng
zong tong hui jin yi bu dui zhong guo zhi cai yao
wo de da gei wo lao po
wo zhi qian du bu zhi dao hai you ge xia ceng di xia shi
bei le hen duo wu
jiu shi zhe le xiong ying ni de xin chao

xie le cao hou men de
zui xin hai wai ying shi ju xia zai
wo men hui ba ni jiu chu lai de
bo sai dong ba wo men an pai dao zhe li qu jiu la ma er
dan ta you pao qi le wo men
la ma er shi bo sai dong de ren bu shi wo men de
yue yu kai shi le
zhe ge bo sai dong dao di shi he fang shen sheng
zhong qing ju li yi ming bu de zhi de zheng ce zhuan jia
ta zai zhong qing ju nei chuang jian le yi ge
jiao er yi hao kong jian de zu zhi
er ta xu yao wo de bang zhu
zai shi jie ge di ba ru yu de ren jiu chu lai
wo men chu fa le yi xie shi
bo sai dong you mei you ke neng rang wo men zhi jie sha le ta
nei yi nan yi nv jiu shi qiang shou
wo men gan jin li kai zhe li
xian zai tao li de wei yi ban fa jiu shi zuo fei ji xiong di
dui bu qi dui bu qi xiong di
wo men de zhua jin xing dong
bu xing wo men jin wan yao shi zou shang jie qu jiu si ding le
ni wo xin zhi du ming
jiu suan chu le jian yu
hai shi jue de zheng ge shi jie du lun wei xia xiao de kong jian
zai jian yu li dai jiu le jiu hui zhe yang
ni yong yuan gan jue zi ji shen zai jian yu li
wo bu neng nei yang sheng huo
wo de zhi dao jian yu gao qiang yi bu fu cun zai
ni nei shi hai pa ni bu ke yao qing xing shi jiu neng gan jue dao
shao na wo ke yao shuo shi
wo bu hui na ni gu er de shen fen shuo shi
wo ye bu hui gao su ni
ni de peng you bing bu shi ni qi dai de fu qin xing xiang
chao shi mei you yong de

wo men yao rang ta men xiao shi dai jin
wo men yao li kai zhe ge guo jia

ni yi jing du shi guo le

na ge du bu yong

ao ma xi ba de ren

wo men neng xin ren ta ma
bu neng dan ta shi wo men zui hou de xuan ze le
ni bei bao shi le ke yi chu yu le
bie dang bu ren shi a tian xin
bo sai dong xian ba ni nong chu lai le
wo yuan yi wei wo cai shi ta de zui ai ni
zhe gou ri de zhen tao chu lai le
dan wei shi yao sha le la ma er wo hai yi wei ta men shi yi huo de
gan wo men zhe xing de bu gai wen de bie wen
huo xu wo men ying gai wen
bo sai dong ming ling wo men zhao dao qia ni er wu ti si sha le ta
zhe cai shi wo men yao zuo de shi
wo xiang wo zhi dao gai zen yao zuo le
ni lai zhe zuo shi yao
dao chu du zai tong qi ni peng you
ni sha le a bu la ma er shi zhen de ma
nei ke bu shi ming zhi zhi ju
ni zhi yao gao su wo men yao qu na
chuan yue sha mo si ba san gong li dao fei a ke si
gan zou si de lao peng you
zi zhi ling di mei you de ren
ni men si ge wo yi ge wei zi bu gou
hao ba hao ba zai nong yi liang che zen yao yang
wo gen ni men shuo a

huo xu wo men neng hu xiang bang zhu
wo hai you yi liang che

wo ben lai yao diu xia ta de
dan ru guo ni men neng ba ta nong lai
ta zai yi ge ju zhe liang ge jie qu de ting che chang
wo hui rang ni men gen zhao de

dao ou zhou fa guo yi da li xi ban ya xiang qu na du xing
zhe zhu yi ru he
zuo bian nei chuang hong zhuan de yi ceng

wei pu ni liu xia gen ta yi qi wo men zou
ta zong shi nei yang gei ni fa hao shi ling ma
yi yan nan jin le
wo you ge ming ling gei ni

ting wo de kou ling yi qi tui

jiu liang ge jie qu yuan mei wen ti
zhi yao you ren shuo mei wen ti jiu yi ding hui chu wen ti
ta gei wo men xia le tao shang che
wo bu shi zhen dui ni huo ji

wo bie wu xuan ze
ni zhe ren zha gan bei hou tou xi wo

dui ni men xu yao wo
wo yao qu zhe ge fei a ke si de di tu
ni zhi dao zhe li shi ye men dui ba
fei a ke si shi ge xiao di fang
quan shi xiao tu wu mei you di tu
dan wo ke yi dai ni men qu
ni yao xiang xin zhe ge ren ma
ru guo ta shua wo men
wo men jiu rang wei pu da si ta
wo jue dui hui sha le ni
wo deng bu ji yao sha ta le
ni gan bei hou tou xi wo wo jiu mie le ni
wo men guo jia de shou yao yuan ze dong ma
wo men guo jia de shou yao yuan ze shi
ru guo da shi bu miao nei jiu qu sha mo
wo men zhen shi zou tou wu lu le
ao ma er bi wo men geng can
ta xian zai re le zui bu gai re de ren jiu shi wei pu
zhe ju hua ye shi yong yu ni mai ke er
wo gan jue nei hai zi jue de ni bei pan le ta
wo ke yi li jie ta wei shi yao zhe yao xiang
wo zhen de hen bao qian huo ji
wo yi hai pa jiu hui zuo cuo xuan ze
lan de ting ni fei hua dong ma
wo zhe ji tian zhen de guo de hen bu shuang bu shuang tou ding le
zheng zai shou shi xin ban gong shi a
wo hai jue de zhe li shi kai le man de ban gong shi chang guan
huo xu ni yi jing zhi dao

ta yi zhi zai diao cha er yi hao kong jian zhe ge zu zhi
shi de wo zhi dao
wo xu yao bao luo de wen jian

qi shi wo diao cha le ta de xian suo

hao jia ru xin de kan fa xing

zhe li guo wu yuan ma
ren he yu zheng ju lian you guan de di fang
mei xiang dao zhe ge shi jian da dian hua guo lai
wo zhi shi xiang ji xu wo men zao xie shi hou de hua ti
zhong dong de qing kuang zen yang le
qing kuang you le bian hua
wo men de jin kuai jian mian
wo men hui qu le jiu gei ni da dian hua
ni zai guo jia an quan ju gong zuo

fang fo kong bu dian ying de dong xi
zhi dao bo sai dong jie chu wo

ai mi li hen gao xing zai ci jian dao ni

guan yu qia ni er wu ti si de

ting wo shuo guan fang hui da shi bu
wo men bu can yu zhong qing ju ji yi qie gong ji xing zhi de xing dong
wo men zhi fu ze jian shi
wo men zhi xiang jian shi ta

rang ni men zuo wei guan cha yuan jia ru
wo jiu zhi dao ni hui bang wo
ke ni qian wo ren qing

ni bu dong fei a ke si ren

dui xin zang mei you hao chu

wo men hui cheng gong di da de

dang wo hui qu hou wo qing ni he yi bei
wo bu he jiu de

wo men zhao dao ta le bu shi ma

ta men bu zhi dao wo men zai jian shi ta men dui ma

yi wei lai zi yuan fang de peng you
ni de zheng fu yi zhi ba wo men shi wei di ren
guan fang shuo fa er yi
dan wo men zhong you ren de xiang fa geng kai ming
a bu la ma er ceng shi yi wei you yuan jian zhuo shi de ren
wo men xiang ni biao shi zui cheng zhi de ai dao
ni xiang yao shi yao
he ni xiang yao de yi yang
chu diao sha le ta de xiong shou
wo men hui gao su ni men ta men de que qie fang wei
ni neng kan jian wo ma
gai si de dian nao she xiang tou
shui zao de zhe gui wan yi er
hao le wo kan jian ni le

gan jin dong shou ba
ni xiang bao chi zhe yang ma
wo men neng gei ni song kai shi ni zou le yun
sha le a bu la ma er de nei xie ren
zheng zai li kai sa nei yan ba ling hao gao su xiang xi xing
wo men xian zai jiu chu fa
zhe bu zai shi ni de zhan dou le

wo shou gou le yan re
wo you dian xi huan zhe li le

fei a ke si zheng shi gai qu de di fang

mei you ke ji ma
fo lai di mo ke rui du hei bu jin qu
fo lai di mo ke rui

shou ji fa ming qian wo ye huo de hao hao de

 ba li ke yi ba

fu ren ta men hai mei fa xian san ge shi zong de deng shan zhe
hui gao su nin zui xin xiao
nei jiu shi zhen zheng de mei guo zong tong
yong yuan zhe yao ku
dang ran wo men hai de tan dao zong tong
fei chang gan xie fang qing song shi yao de
dan shi yao duan yi dian
ran hou jiu jia ru wo dui wei lai de yuan jing
xian zai xian biao ji shang wei lai sui bian ba
you ge qing bao jian bao hui yi
wo de can jia hao ma
wo men ying gai pai hao you xian shun xu
yin wei you xue jian zeng jia kai zhi
fu ren wo bu neng pei nin qu zhe ge qing bao jian bao hui yi
wo you nin yao de he lan yan yao shui
bu wo bu xu yao ni
hao de wo jiu jue de de wen wen zhe shi nin de ka fei
rang fu zong tong can jia zhe xie hui yi ma
wo bu xiang rang ta xiang wo dang fu zong tong shi
you nei xie shi yi yang de jing li
yi han de shi zong tong yi jing ding hao yao can jia zhe ge hui yi le
suo yi wo bu xiang gai bian shi qing
zhe zhong zao qi jie duan bu
zong tong xu yao zhe ge bao
mei zhe yao jian dan hai hai qing yi dian
ni na de bu dui ni na de bu dui
gu niang men du ku le pi tiao ke kuai si le
wo jiu jue de ting dao yi ge xiao nv hai de sheng yin
gen wo lai xian zai zhe li shi nan ren bang le
bu hui zai you run fu lu he fu yan ji de e chou le
nei hai zhi shi de wei dao er yi
da ge zi ni zhe sha diao hai hao ma
ting hao jiu xiang jia ding ri lai dao le se qing di lao
jian ru pan shi man shi mi zhi
ni xi huan ma wo you yi da dui huang duan zi
ni zhe sha diao hai hao ma
cu da de rou gun
e fu zong tong xian sheng nin hao
gan xie nin rang wo guo lai
ni zhi dao shi shui da ying le zhan zheng ma
wo xiang xin shi wo men
bu bu shi qian xian de bu dui
shi mu hou de ren men
qing bao ren yuan jie mi ren yuan
wo yao ni zuo wo zai xi yi de qie ting qi
wo yao ni wei wo ci tan qing bao
leng cang ni le lao gu dong
jue dui de nve dai xun huan ji xu jin xing
jiu xiang tian zhu jiao tang
an zhi jiao tang luan tong nan hai men chang da le you ji xu luan tong
shi de huo zhe a ken se zhou de hun li
a ken se zhou shi xing qi yue hun yin jie hun ma fan li hun ye ma fan wu guo cuo bu de li hun
jiu zhe xie xie xie ni
shi de xian sheng xie xie nin xian sheng
ta shi ge hao hai zi
suo yi ni tao yan wo shi ma
kai wan xiao ni wo men shi xiong
dan wo shi fu zong tong de mu liao chang
ni pao lai zhi jie jian ta
wo du bu zhi dao ni yao lai
qian wo bu shi xiang
bu shi wo bu shi xiang yue ji
bu wo men mei shi wo men shi yong yuan de peng you
hao de tai hao le xie xie
ni shi ge hao ren
wo men xu yao ni zhe yang de ren yin wei zhe ge you xi xu yao yong qi
ni du you peng you
fu zong tong xi huan ni
wo hen gao xing ta xi huan bie ren
xia ci lai zhi qian gei wo fa duan xin
wo du hui rang ni jin de
wo bu xiang he de ji hua bang zai yi qi
yi ge si ren de ji hua
ta hai mei si fu ren

jia ting di yi de zui xin min yi diao cha
shu ju zen yao yang
fu yang hai zi tuo li pin kun bang zhu you gong zuo de ma ma
yin wei mou xie yuan yin pin kun de you gong zuo de ma ma xi huan ta

tong chang shi tou gei qi ta bu hui chang ge de pin kun nian qing ma ma

jun dui zen yao yang
ni men ren wei ta men hui zhi chi geng duo de xue jian ma
wo men zhi yao nong ge ding
ni shuo shi yao ding

wo men ti chu yi ge ji jin de jun dui xue jian ti an

ya zi qu si ba
zong tong fu ren hui zhao dao ban fa

ye xu wo men ke yi ba a fu han gua shang
bin zhou de shu ju

er dang wo men xiang dao wo men de hai zi
wo xiang zhe ge ban ben hai bao han
zong tong de lao de zeng jia kai zhi ji hua
wo men jiang yao tou zi liu bai yi mei yuan
jian she xin de liu er ling xing qian ting
dui zhe ge zhi guan zhong yao de xian dai hua fang yu xi tong
zeng jia yi bai yi mei yuan tou zi
ta gang xuan bu le yi ge si ren de ji hua
ta hai mei ta ma de si ni
ni jue de ta zhu yi dao le ma
wo ta miao de du de shi ge shi yao gui
ni men ying gai ba qian ting xue jian qu diao
bu shi zai ta men shen shang duo hua yi bai yi
wo shuo zhe ge yan jiang
ben lai ying gai wan mei di ding yi wo de ren qi
xiu yi xia hao ma
xu duo cheng shi de hai zi
ben lai ke yi mian yu pin kun
xian zai bu ran zhe xie qian
jiang hui yong yu jian zao guo shi de
jin shu de ju da de jia ding ri
ni men zhi dao bu zhi dao
ni men li wo yue yuan yue hao
gun chu wo de ban gong shi
fu ren wo zhi dao nin xian zai xian zai xu yao du chu
zhi shi zhe xie qian guo de
wo jiu wo jiu fang zai zhe
bao qian fu ren nin shuo bu xiang bei da rao
dan shi wo men you ge an pai zai xian zai de jing xuan hui yi
zong tong fu ren wo zhi dao nin gan wo chu qu
dan shi wo men de wu ren ji gang gang zai ye men zha cuo ren le
wo qu xie ge bao gao
zong tong fu ren bao qian da rao
xiang gao su nin liang ge deng shan zhe bei fa xian si wang
qing ni li kai hao ma
dui bu qi zong tong fu ren
deng deng shi yao deng shan zhe
shi yao deng shan zhe
bie bi wo jin tian qu shang ban
wei le tao ban wo lian jia si du gan de chu lai
ni zhe chang xiang bu pei you yi yu zheng a
gong zuo liang hai you zong shi zai jiao dian zhi
di yi fa an bei ma can
min zhong hen si nei wan yi le
shi a nei wan yi jiu xiang ge bei za guo de hun li dan gao yi yang si fen wu lie
zong tong xiang rang wo zhao shou
cu shi mei ti ba ta cheng zuo fa an
ran er ta men jue ding jiao ta ma mi fa an
gong zuo shi ren zuo de
na zhao zhe cha zi tong wo de jing dong mai gei wo ge tong kuai ba
ni shi zhe ge shi jie shang zui you ying xiang li de xiao ming le
zong tong ke shi yin ni cai ying le ta di yi chang bian lun a
ni cai zen yao zhao hai you liang chang ni
er qie jie xia lai yi chang yu wai jiao zheng ce you guan
kao shi fan wei shi quan shi jie bu hua zhong dian
gai zen yao zhun bei a
ni yao shuai diao bao fu hao ma
bao chi zhen ding dai shang xiao lian
jin tian hui shi ni ren sheng zhong zui kuai le de yi tian
hui jian ai yo wo cao a sheng ri kuai le
bao qian wo mei you shi jian gei ni mai li wu le
wo shi shi xia ban hou xing bu xing
wo zhu zai zhen shi de mei guo zhong yi tiao pu tong de jie dao shang
zhe er you zhen shi de shu mu he qi che
de jie dao shang de que you zhen shi de che
wo bu zhi dao jia che shi ge shi yao dong xi
qiao wo de zong tong fan er ya
ru guo ta yi zao mei he jiu xian zai ye gai yi he jie qian chou le
e shang di ni zhi dao wo ying gai ti qi shi yao ma
de nv er zai da xue li gei
yi piao gan lan qiu yun dong yuan chui la ba de chuan wen
nei ni jiu yao fan cuo wu lou
da cuo te cuo ming ming shi chang qu gun qiu yun dong yuan
nv shi nin jin ri wan can de lai bin du yi jing que ren hao le
fang song zhi ye yi jing suo ding bu bian
hao lei wo jian zhi deng bu ji le
jin wan wo yao he yi qian de xiao bang pai zhong ju
jiu shi nian dai de shi hou an na bo li si wan quan jiu shi wo men ji ge jie men er de di pan
ni men du you bang pai wen shen ma
mei jin jin shi wo lao shi wu suo de yi qun lv shi er yi
ni shi zen yao jia ru zhe ge bang pai de
shi bu shi de sha ge ren dang tou ming zhuang
ni xian zai ke yi zong tong she mian zi ji le
yao zhi dao zuo wei nv xing shi ji shang zhe shi zao jiu gao ding le
jia shang wo men de feng ru fei tun
zhen shi mi si ge ren yao feng de feng yao yu de yu
pi zi bao fa sheng le yi qi qiang ji
gong si ren si wang bao kuo kai qiang zhe
hao ba zhe ta ma bu tai hao a
wo men wei wang zhe de jia ting qi fu
dui a er qie hai xi wang ta men bu yao qiu geng duo de qiang xie guan zhi
zhe li shuo kai qiang zhe shi tui wu hai jun
ben gai bao jia wei guo que qu shang hai min zhong zhen shi bei ai
hei rang qi cao yi fen sheng ming
ta you ban fa yi ji qi dao zhe mo ban
wo men jie zhao lai kan wo ba
mei guo hun ning tu lian bang hui yi
dang wo li kai bai gong de shi hou
wo cong lai mei xiang dao wo hui lai wei hun ning tu you shuo
e shun ti yi xia ming tian wo gei wo lia an pai le
liang ge zao wu can he yi ge wu can
e shang di wo ming tian yi jing you liang ge zao can hui le
ru guo wo zai ji xu zhe yang xia qu de hua wo de zui ba yao sheng tong feng le
 nv shi men ni men jiang cheng wei wo men de xiao shou you er
e ni shuo de you er zhi de shi
xiang ni men zhe yang du li zi zhu jie shou guo liang hao jiao yu
xing gan re la de nian qing nv xing neng ba yi yuan men yin you dao xiao hei wu li qu
zai mou zhong fang mian lai jiang zhe jiu shi nv quan zhu yi
jin jie zhao wo men hui jie shao wo men de ke hu ta men zuo cheng mai mai
cong mou zhong fang mian lai jiang zhe jiu shi zi ben zhu yi
wo bu xu yao he ren he ren zuo ren he shi dui ba
zhe shi you shuo shi ge zhi de zun jing de zhi ye
bang wo ge mang qu nei bian zhao
ta you ji jian shao jin de chen shan ni ke yi huan yi xia
suo yi ni lia zhun bei hao he hun ning tu xin xin xiang ying le ma
shi de hei wei shi yao zhe ge hun ning tu huo dong de lie biao shang
you zhe yao duo an bao he jun dui de ren
wo men shi zai he nian tu da zhang yao
jun dui jing chang mai shi yao
e wo zhi dao tang guo
you mai meng da an shi hun ning tu
suo yi wo men dai zhao jun dui de ren
rang ta men zha chu guo hui de qian
xiu jian mo xi ge bian jing de hun ning tu qiang zhe jiu shi sheng cun zhi dao
tong shi fu wu hao ji ge ke hu qun
wo jiu xi huan zhe
jian zhi tai lang le bu shi ma
zhe er jiu shi ge zhao huang piao yang de mao pian xian chang
shang di a sha le wo ba
zao shang hao zao shang hao
rang wo men kai shi pa ti
ma mi fa an shi fou zhu ding shi bai
shou xian zhe bu shi ma mi fa an
zhe shi jia ting di yi bu zhe shi fa an
ta he wo dui tian tian quan de ai yi yang zhu ding chi jiu
wo men neng xian tao lun xia jia ting di yi fa an ma
yi ta hui ding zai shan shang de chi ru zhu
wo de zhong yao fa an
nan dao ni ren wei wo hui shuo zhe ge
bu shi he ran hou ba ta na dao tao bao shang dang er shou mai diao ba
ao bu lai en yi yuan shuo ru guo jia ting di yi fa an tong guo le
jia ting de zheng ge gai nian du hui zhong jie
zhe ken ding shi wo men de meng xiang a
dan wo bu que ding shi fou neng zai zhe yi dai shi xian
wo bu guan ao bu lai en shi bu shi tao yan ta
zhe shi wei le nei xie xi huan ta de ren zhi ding de
dui dan hai shi bu dui sha
wo bu xiang shuo wo zui jie di qi le
dan wo que shi shi pu tong ren zhi yuan yi
wei ta men zi ji de er bu shi qi ta ren de jia ting fu chu
zhe ke bang bu shang
nv shi zhe er you ge ru qin zhe wo men xu yao ni dai zai zhe er
shi yao wo shi shuo hao wo shuo zhe shi zen yao hui shi
wo ke mei liao dao zhe shi zhe shi wo mei liao dao
ying you er du wu du bi ni hui zao ju su si bo shi dai mao zi de mao zuo zhe
ling huo de shi jian dui da jia du you li
zhe shi yi ge chang shi
you ru qin zhe da jia bao chi leng jing
dai zai yuan di bie dong
hao de quan mian feng suo ba mei ren dong jiu mei ren shou shang
wo men xian zai bu ying gai shi zai qu di xia mi shi de dian ti zhong ma
zhe li mei you dian ti ye mei mi shi
wei shi yao zhe li mei you yi ge tong xiang mi shi de dian ti
ni shai kang de gen yi tiao zai keng li shi jing la shi de gou yi yang
wo zhen xin jue de wo ying gai you yi ba qiang
wo bing mei you zai shuo xiao wo shi zhen de xu yao yi ba qiang
hao nei wo men ni you mei you yi ge kong huang fa sheng shi yong de an quan shi shi yao de
ni zou na er du shi kong huang shi
xu yao zhao dao yi ge geng an quan de fang
sha diao he nei ge jian
nei ge ru qin zhe jiu zai nei er
wo de tian yi yu cheng chen yi yu cheng chen yi yu cheng chen a
ni zai zuo shi yao
ni na zhong zuo shi yao gao su ta ta lai wan le
xie xie ni xian sheng
bao qian wo yao chu qu tou tou qi

ta zai shuo shi yao ni ting dao ta shuo shi yao le ma

ta shuo le shi yao
ta shuo rang wo qi lai
wo xiang sha diao he nei ge jian ren
ta lai zhe jiu shi wei le sha wo
que lian wo de ming zi du bu zhi dao
wo de qu hao hao niao yi da pao
lao tian zhe ge ru qin shi jian ba wo xia niao le
jiu xiang shi gou tu ren yan nei yang de liang xia
hao le yi yuan wo yao qu zhun bei ni de shi zheng ting hui yi le
hao ya li biao sheng
wo bu gan xiang xin you ren hui lai zhe er ci sha wo
ni shen bian hai shi you hen duo hao ren pei zhao ni de

wo zhi jie mian dui ta ran hou wo jiu
hou tui ge men bie re mao wo
shen shang xian su yi jing biao de bu xing
wo gan jue wo bi xu zuo dian er shi yao
gei wo nong xie ka fei ma

hai ni zai na er ni neng bu neng que bao zhe xie qi zi
he mu bu dui cheng ni
kan qi lai you dian pian le

wo xi huan zhe gan jue tai bang le
wo men gan de piao liang a hei deng guang
hai jin zhan ru he neng ba deng guang shao wei diao an yi dian dian ma
hao ba si hu zhe xiao guo you dian guo tou le

hen hao  ji xia ta

wo bu xiang zi kua de

huo ji men zhe shi

wa e ni ken ding hen xing fu ye hen fu you

ye jiu shi shuo ta de he yi yuan tan tan
dan bu shi xian zai che qi de ta
a xiang xiang nian qing ge er ling sui ba shi ba
wo hai chuan zhao niao bu

wo men cuo guo shi ji
wo neng kan chu lai ni he wo men yi yang

wo xiang jie shao xian sheng gei nin ren shi
kan jiu xiang zhe yang
que fa jiao yu he pin qiong zhi jian

pin qiong he fan zui zhi jian ye shi ru ci

ta zhuo jue qun lun
jiu xiang ba ba la shi cui shan chang gao yin yi yang bu fei li
wo de tian ni zai na chu sheng de ji lao hu ma mei guo ren xiang xin nan tong zhi du ai ba ba la
jin zao pi zi bao fa sheng qiang ji an hou
ni ren wei shi shi hou yan ge kong zhi qiang zhi le ma
ying dui cuo shi hen jian dan
zhen zheng li jie que hen nan
xiong shou nan dao bu ye shi yi wei shou hai zhe ma
wo men suo tao lun de ke shi yi wei tui yi hai jun

shen a gen wo lai

zong tong nv shi nin neng
que ding gang cai nin suo shou dao de wei xian deng ji shi duo shao ma

zhe ke shi wo jin tian

yu yan bing bu neng sha ren
qiang que bu yi yang

zhe shi hen bu hao de shi fei chang bu hao
wo ke yi ji xu

shi a hao shi du hui gan shang ni de

zhe yao yi lai ta de zheng zhi nao dai bei da kai le hua
shi a ta gang xiang suo you you qiang de sha men

ta men dao di wei shi yao yao fu zhe yao duo qian gei wo men

kan kan zhe ge hun dan ta yi jing ding shang wo le
wo men ke yi rang ta shang
pi ping tong qing sha ren fan
rang wo men wu xu can yu ren he wu yi de qiang zhi bian lun
gan de piao liang ni ke neng shi
wo gei guo qian de nv ren li zui cong ming de le
ni zhi dao ma wo lai ban yi jing gao ding le

xiang shou ni men xiong mei zhi jian de zhe zhong jing zheng
wo zai xiang nei ni dui yu wo men lai shuo shi shi yao
wo yi hui er da gei ni
wo zai nei er kuai si le zhe chao chu le wo de kong zhi
suo yi zhen de you shi yao qing kuang zai ni de kong zhi zhi zhong ma
hao ba bu gu hou guo wo xing wo su

wo bu shi mei lin mo fa shi hao ma

shi shi shang bu wo

ru guo ni zuo le cuo shi
ni bi xu li ke jiu zheng cuo wu
wo shuo shi yao du wu fa bang zhu
shou hai zhe de qin ren men

wo zhen de zhen de hen bao qian
wo bu neng shuo gan jue hen hao

tai bang le he hao shen qi sheng de hai

hao ba gan xie fan kui

wo men ying gai qing nin ti wo men suo you gao za de shi zhi qian

e shi de nv hai nei jian shi

hai fa sheng le ling wai yi qi shu ju wai xie shi jian
wo jue de mei you
mei you yin wei ru guo you wo hui zhi dao de
huo ji men yao da che hui hua sheng dun ma
wo ke yi ting ni men jiang jiang di yi xian de gu shi
nei yi ding hen lai jing
wo hen le yi dan wo you shi yao hui yi an pai ma
ni que ding mei you ren he an pai

zhan zheng de qian xian
hen gao xing ren shi ni hai you ni ben jie ming
wo xi wang xia ci jian mian shi zhuang kuang neng hao xie
dai wo men tong guo guan
wo men lia mei guo ren mei you ni wo lia sha du ban bu cheng
wo ke bu xiang zi sha
gei wo zhao dao qiu chang
wo jiu gei ni qian
kan yi xia ni de you xiang sha la
wo kan de zhe shi shi yao
yi ge xi ren si nian qian pai de zhao pian
yong yi zhong gua zai shu shang de yun dong chuan gan qi
ke yi jian xie xing pai she xi wu
you yi tian zao chen xi ren chu men fa xian le zhe xie tu pian

di er tian jiu you xie ji zheng ju le

ta xia fei ji shi wo men cha dian jiu zhua zhu ta le

que ru ci mei li dong ren
ni bu shi zai dong shi yao huai zhu yi ba nai si xian sheng
wo men shi yi huo de sha la
ni gei wo shan kai bu ran wo jiu han le
wo zui bu xi wang nei yang le
bu fang xian ting ting wo shuo de
wo zhi dao qia ni er wu ti si de shi
shuo shuo ni du zhi dao shi yao
wo cong fu ke si he jian yu xing man shi fang nei tian
you ge jiao wu ti si de ren
zhu dong juan gei wo zhe ge xin shi yi zhi
zhi yi bai wan mei yuan ma
wei shi yao hui you ren dui wo zhe zhong bei bi xiao ren qing nang xiang zhu ni
yi fen du bu ke neng geng bie shuo yi bai wan le
ru guo ni shi lai zhao wo yao da an de hua wo wu ke feng gao
wo zhao guo da an le sha la yi sheng
wo zai wang shang cha xun le wu ti si zhe ge ren
jie guo chu xian le ni yi gu qian fu de lian
kan zhao sheng long huo hu zhao ni
la sa lu si er fu sheng le
ta shi bu shi xiang la wo men qu zuo shi yao shi
ta shi bu shi xiang yao shi yao dong xi
ni yao shi zai jie jin wo huo shi wo de jia ren wo jiu sha le ni
wo men zui hao zhan zai tong yi zhan xian shang sha la
wo men ke yi yi qi jie jue de
wo men du ting shuo le wai mian de zhan zheng
dan shi jiu suan zhi zai gao qiang zhi nei
zhe ge guo jia de fa lv reng ran jian zai
zhen zhu zhi fa bi ran qu dai zhe fu xiu zhi guo de fa lv
wo men bu hui zai tui hua hui dong wu
ni hai xin ren ta zhen shi bu ke si yi
ta hui li yong ni yue yu ran hou jiu shuai le ni
mei you ren yao yue yu
ni shi shi yao ren
zhe ge jian yu li zui le jie ni peng you de ren
wo gen ta yi qi guan jin bi hao duo nian
dan ni mei bei guan guo ta dui mian de jin bi shi
ta gen wo shuo guo yue yu de shi qing
ta ceng shi tu shuo fu wo gen ta yi qi yue yu
zhi you wo men liang ge ren
dan shi wo ju jue le ta
wo shi bu hui li kai wo xiong di de
wo ti nei reng liu tang zhao jun ren de xie
ye liu tang zhao ji du tu de xie
ta shi ge ji hui zhu yi zhe
ta hui li yong ren he ta suo xu yao de ren
wo zhi dao ta yi gen ni shuo guo yue yu de shi le
ni gen ta zai yi ge lao fang li ni
ni gao su wo wo jiu neng bang ni
gan zai ta li yong ni ba nei ge da mo tou nong chu jian yu
que ba wo men liu zai zhe li deng si zhi qian
wo men xu yao hu zhao ao ma ni neng bang wo men ma
deng deng wo men neng xin de guo zhe jia huo ma
ta ke shi tou wo hu zhao zai xian de ren
nei ke shi cheng xin jiao yi peng you
wo shi yao du mei de dao
zai shuo ni de hu zhao zao mei le
wo gu ji xian zai yi jing yuan zai tian bian le

ni hai you bie de xuan ze ma
kuai jue ding wo yao li kai zhe zuo cheng shi le
zhe li yi jing mei you di fang shi an quan de le

ni ben ke yi lan wo dan ni xuan ze bu lan

ni cai zhu lao hu de de bo zi

ni xuan ze lai zhe de yuan yin wo yao ti xing ni yi xia
ni jiu bu ying gai lai zhe er
mei shi yao neng zu zhi wo lai
xian zai wo men san ge du zai ta shou shang
xiang kan kan ta ma
dang wo zhi dao zi ji huai yun de shi hou
ni gang hao fa xian lai di hai huo zhao
suo yi wo jue ding deng lai di he ni du mi yue hui lai
zai gao su ni hai zi de shi
ran hou wo hai mei you ji hui jiu bei ta zhua le
ta qi ming zi le ma
wo qi de jiao ma ke si
dan nei shi ta de zhong jian ming
ta da ming ying gai you ta ba ba lai qu
wo hen bao qian duo mu
ni mei shi yao hao bao qian de

wo zhi wo zhi dao ni zai xiang shi yao
wo ba jing wei du zhi kai le

ai lin nuo shi ge jing cha mei zhun ni men lia
