kai tou lai yi ge guan yu dang di da ka de xiao hua bi ru xian chang de bu lu ke shi chang
ke neng xiao guo hui hen hao
bi ru ta de ai zheng nei hui ta de yi sheng bu de bu qie chu
ta cao zi ji jia bao mu de neng li
tai can ku le ba
wo le jie xin han bu shi er de xi su xin wo zhe shi ge da xiao dian
xian sheng yi xie wo men du mei yong guo de le dui
fa lai yi xie jing gao han
si ting bu lu si si pu lin si ting
fa lai liang feng hai you en ya
gei ta fa yi feng jing gao han ba
hao xie er man nv
wo hai ji de ni gei ni ma ma de nei fu
yong kong xin mian pin de xiao xiang hua
wo ke bu ji de shi yao kong xin mian hua xiang xie er man nv shi
yi si nv shi gai ni chu chang
wo men di yi wei yan jiang zhe zhu di xie er man nv shi
ni ting jian ta yong kong xin fen hua xiang chao feng wo le ma
ni ta ma neng xiang xin ma
wo men xian zai you da wei ji le
zong tong xian zai shi yao feng yan feng yu du ting xin kuai lai
ni man dian wo zui jin zai chi ke mai ding
su wo men yao jian zong tong
xian sheng men ni men xian ca ca han nai xin deng dai yi xia ba
gen bie ren tan hua
bie you yu jiu cha li le
bu guo hua shuo hui lai yuan zhu ni de nan peng you
hui bu hui jie shu ni de zhi ye sheng ya a
dan you ba qiang di zai ni de tou shang
huo xu qiang li mei you zi dan a
gan xie ni de lai fang
wo de rong xing xian sheng men
ta zhen shi pi yong mei you
nv shi wo men de zuo chu zui hou jue ding le
ji shi ta shi cuo wu jue ding
wo jiu zai xu yao yi diu diu shi jian
ru guo ming tian zao shang wo men hai na bu chu zhi xing fang an
zhou yi wo men jiu bian cheng xi la le
guo jia xi la bu shi yin le ju xi la
hao wo de zui zhong jue ding shi
ming tian zao shang ni men hui shou dao yi ge zui zhong jue ding
zuo hao liang shou zhun bei
xian zai wo yao gen yi se lie zong li dian hua hui tan
jie zhao hai you fa guo zong tong hao ma
shuo bu ding ta men neng gei wo dian jian yi ni
nv shi yu qi zhe yang bu ru ting ting wo de zhu yi
ni xian zai shi yao du bie xiang gai zha wan er zha wan er
wo hui da dian hua gei qiao na he
ran hou ni jiu ba ta men ma de lai zhao bu zhao bei
dan shi dang he ni yi qi du guo le si qi nian de zhang fu
zai bing ta qian wen ni shi
dan xian zai zong tong yao gen ni tong dian hua
dan wo zhen te yao bu gan xiang xin
ni ba gong zuo zheng de yi tuan zao
ni xian zai wei le diao gao shui shou he wai yin qie kai shou zhu
er ben bo yan jiang ma
nv shi wo men xu yao yi dian shi jian
rang shi jie shang zui gao nei tuo la ji jie dian hua
wo bu zhi dao ni mei tian bu mang zhao ying fan er zai xia bi mang shi yao
dan shi ken ding gen pi gu he ju hua you guan xi
ni xian zai xue xue zen yao kong zhi ni nei tian diao de pi qi
fou ze wo jiu hui qin zi xian shen
ran hou zou de ni man di zhao ya
sai lin nuo mei ye jiu shi ge ping yong zhi bei
ta de wei yi cheng jiu jiu shi yi shou gao kua le jing ji
zen yao wo men cheng le hu xiang tian ju de sha diao le
ta de zong tong sheng ya jiu shi yi ge jie yi ge de chi ru
lai du bu zun zhong
ma de gong zuo hai zuo de bu hao ma
shuo zhen de yan jing a shi yao du gao zhao a
yue kan yue shun yan zhen shi ge hao zhu yi
qu ni de zhen tao yan
wo bao zheng wo bu hui rang ren he ren
hui huo ni xin xin ku ku de xie han qian
ni gei wo shang qu
hao hao di zhen she yi xia xin han bu shi er
hua gang yan zhi zhou ni men hao ma
huo zhe qi shi zhao dao le
ni ge song huo gun hui hua sheng dun ba
wo an pai le yi xie ji jin fen zi
er qie wo de zhi wei fei chang gao zhi ze hen zhong da
ni shi sai lin nuo mei ye gao kua zhe ge guo jia de bang xiong
ba guo jia gao kua shi sai lin nuo zi ji zuo de hao ma
bu wo shi ren zhen de
zhe bi kan wo zi ji hai zi chu sheng
dui ta yi ge ren jiu wan quan gao kua le jing ji
dan shi ta gen ben bu zai hu
yin wei ta zheng mang zhao gen da kuan nan peng you bao bao ni
wo bu zhi dao ni men zen yang
fan zheng wo de nan peng you ke bu shi da kuan
ta de zheng ge zong tong ren qi jiu shi cong yi ge chi ru zou xiang ling yi ge chi ru
bu zhi dao ni shi bu shi shou gou le
wo ke bu da suan zai ji xu ni lai shun shou xia qu le
wo shi qiao na rui an
wo yao zuo ni men de yi yuan
wo bu hui tui suo xie xie

ta zhen de jing shen cuo luan le
ta zheng zai xiang ni ke song de fang xiang fa zhan
ni jue de shi shui shuo de

ai mi hen you ke neng ni de diao cha

ni qu gen cai zheng cai zheng bu shuo

hei nv shi wo zhi dao ni gen cha li zai yi qi shi dui de

wo hai kan zhong le yi ben

wo yao yong tuan gou quan

bu shou tuan gou quan zong gong yi ba si yi er mei yuan

ta ran le hu zi ma
yi que bao ta men zhang wo le
wo le ge da cao ta ran le hu zi

wo men xian zai chu le tai duo lou zi le

ta you hen bang de zu zhi neng li

ta ta gan de piao liang

o ta jiu bu neng zhi da dian hua lai yao
wo jue de wo chuan yue dao wei lai le

a xin hao bu hao ni shuo yi ge zi lou yi ge zi ni

ni zhe yao yi shuo jiu li ke cheng quan le wo de hao ri zi er hui le ta de

ting zhao qing ting zhao
ru guo you ren bu zhi dao
xiao wei man he chang ling hua de qu bie de de hua jiu ke yi li kai le hao ma
de zao xing shi shou dao wo de bei zhu le yao
hao tai hao le e tian a
zhe shi cong liu lang han de fen tou ba lai de yao

xi huan de ren er zai zhe er
wo zui ai de bai gong she jiao mi shu
ni ting shuo le zhuo shang bai jian de shi le yao
ting shuo le wo ting shuo ni ba ta tui le rang ta zhuang shi di yu qu le
jiu shi shuo a wo men jue de nei jiu shi bu dui tou
suo yi zhe shi zong tong de yi jian
zhe shi wo men de yi jian

e bu cuo a yin wei mou xie ren yi wei
ni shi xin de jing xuan jing li ni

gan xie nin de re qing ying jie
hao le wo bu shi xiang da cha
dan shi dao ci wei zhi ba xie xie
suo yi wo men xiu xi wu fen zhong ran hou ji xu
wo xi huan ta wo ke tao yan zheng ke le
zong tong nv shi bai gong de yi fu hua jin tian bei yi chu le

zhe shi zheng dong da lou li wei yi de yin di an ren yi zhu pin
wo shi shuo shui zhi dao wo men you nei ge a
nei ge hua le xie fa dian de san jiao xing de hua
yin di an ren jue de ta men shou dao le dai man
nei jiu fa ge shen ming shuo wo men zhi shi ba ta song chu qu qing xi
dui le rang zuo zhe jian shi
yin wei wo da suan rang qu dai ni
guan yu suo jian feng suo yi zhi xing ke xing xing
de shi shi tao lun bao gao

er ling dao da du ta jiao xing le wo men zhi you si fen zhong le
hao dui bu qi wo mei kong
lai gen ni jie shi wo dui nei ge de xiang fa
wo nao zi li du shi zhong dong de shi ni
ji shi wo men you xie guan dian bu tong
wo ren wei wo ma ma tui dong he ping tan pan zhe shi
fei chang de le bu qi
zhen de shi fei chang le bu qi
wo xiang gen ni tan xie si ren wen ti
wo mei gen nei xie jia huo xi du
wo zhi shi zai ta men de da ba li dai le ban ge xiao shi
zhe shi xing xiang pin pai wen ti
wo rang ni lai shi yin wei
mei guo bu xi huan ni
zhe ting qi lai tai can ku le dian
tou ban biao ti ban de zong jie ci
bu dai biao ni bu tao ren xi
zhi shi yi zhong guan dian shuo ni bu tao ren xi huan
wo bu hui yong hen zhe ge ci ni zhi shi
liang ji hua de guan dian er zhe yi tou bi jiao zhong
ni jian bang ting xue de
zhe jiu xiang shi gao zhong zhong yan
dui you dian er ba gui mo geng da le
rang wo men lai tan tan zhuan bian ni de xing xiang de wen ti ba
de dao gong zhong ren ke de jie jing you
fu yi huo zhe sheng hai zi
hao ba tian a cai bu lao tian ye a wo cai bu zhao ni shuo de nei yang zuo
hao ba rang wo men hui dao xiang ban fa zhuan bian
cheng wei bu ku lian de wen ti shang
suo yi ni cong lai du mei you xiang guo
wo hui jia ru tan hua
hao le ni kan ni jiu zuo zai nei li ting wo zhi hui
ru guo wo xu yao ni bang zhu wo hui gei ni ge xin hao
mei you sha xin hao
yi yuan jian dao ni hen gao
hai xiao pei gen ni dou ge sha zhe shi wo da zhao hu de fang shi huo luo xia qi fen
wo xi huan ni de ban gong shi zhe zhen bang
ni bu zhi jia ju de fang shi
zhe ge qi ma de ren nei ge hua
zhe shi wo lai guo de zui bang de ban gong shi le
wo zhe wei peng you ting xing fen de
jiu hao xiang wo men du wei zhe ge jia ting di yi ti an xing fen yi yang
te bie shi zhe ge xian qi ji hua
te bie zhen dui di shou ru jia ting wo men ji li tui chong zhe bu fen
wo suo dai biao de ren min
xi huan kan dao qian hua de hen ming zhi
dang ran le suo yi wo men yi zhi ti chang bu neng qiong jiao yu
ni dong de bu yao zhi ba ta men dang hai zi
er yao dang cheng xiao ren xing chuang ye gong si
ni dong de hua qian ji shi cun qian
ran hou ni jiu ke yi ba ni cun de qian na chu lai hua le
zhe jiu shi jing ji xue
hao ba zai wo de zhuo shang
ni kan wo cun le yi he you hui quan
wo zi ji jian de e

ni zhi dao zhe li mian hao xie du guo qi le yao

ta jiu zai ta hou mian ta jue bu hui kan dao ta
dan deng deng ta nei yang da bai yi ge yi tiao tui de nan ren
kan qi lai hui hao ma
bu kan qi lai bu hao

ni de rang ta man xia lai

dan wo hui jing xuan zong tong

dan yu ci tong shi hen ming xian wo wu fa liu zhu mei ge ren
suo yi ru guo ni men xu yao xun zhao qi ta gong zuo
nei yao ni men de kai shi si kao le
xian zai mei ren zai xiang nei ge nv shi
wo men cong wei xiang guo zhe jian shi
wo reng zai xiao hua zhe tiao xiao xi
bu guo wo hen xu yao jie zhe ge dian hua
e ni dui ci fen gong zuo de tou ru
e wu  hen ji li ren
ta bu shi jie dian hua ta shi zai da dian hua dui ba
neng qing ni zhuan gao zhou chang
yi jing zhun bei hao he liao yi chang le
ni hao can yi yuan ni hao ma
ni zhen de ren wei ta hui li kai ma
tian nei tai yi han le
bu nei biao shi wo wan quan mei huo gan
wo gang cai shi wei ta yi han
yi yang zhe da gai biao shi
wo men ke yi you geng duo de shi jian zai yi qi
wo men man man lai
fei chang gan xie nin zai zhe yao duan de shi jian nei neng jie jian wo xian sheng
wo de rong xing xiao jie
wo shi ni xiao lv he jing que du de kuang re chong bai zhe
e hao nei yang de hua jin ru zheng ti ba
hen hao wo zun zhong ni de jian ji
zhe du you dian duo duo bi ren le
shi de guo hui yi yuan
huo zhe wo gai shuo dao shi
shi de xian sheng e wo yi zhi jiang nin shi wei dao shi
wo ba ba de fu qin xing xiang tai guai yi ye tai yao yuan le
jiu xiang nei wan ni liu su di er tian zao shang wo men yi qi kan bao zhi de shi hou
wu nei hen bu cuo
wo xiang e nei shi
wo jin hou yi bei zi du ke yi zuo de shi qing
e ni zhi dao wo xi huan shui jue he bao zhi
he bie de ren yi yang dan mei cuo
jin hou yi bei zi
ni zhi dao ni hui de ru chuang
ba ni an pai dao wo de
tong ji meng xiao zu li zen yao yang
mei wen ti xian sheng wo men da cheng yi zhi le
wo men gao ding le hen rong xing he nin gong shi xian sheng
shi de shi de fa guan nin hao ma
fei chang gan xie nin hui dian hua gei wo
ni hen kuai e mei cuo
jiao wo hua sheng dun shan
hao ba rang wo men gan jin pao yi bian ba
dui zhe ge sha da er bi lai shuo ke bu rong yi
ta dong qi lai jiu xiang shi
hei ni dong qi lai xiang shi yao
wo jiu xiang mi xi xi bi jing cha
zhen cha nian qing hei ren mou sha an yi yang man zhong zu qi shi zui chou ming zhao zhu de nan fang zhou zhi yi
mei cuo zhun bei hao le ma
 wan e nin xian qing
hei nv shi nin zhi dao zhe ge xiao xi hui
rang zong tong xin sui
wo xi wang wo ke yi qiao duan ta de ji zhu
dan wo bu neng yin wei ta shi yong guo dong zuo de mei gu qi
bie zhe yang nin dang fu zong tong shi mei guo you shi yi lai zui bang de shi qing
bu mei you jiu shi de wo bu gan le
e fu zong tong nv shi wo zhi qian gao su ni shi yao le
bao qian zheng yao qu jian zong tong
e bu bu ni bu neng ta qu xiao le
qu er dai zhi de shi gen wo jian mian
nv shi wo zhi qian zheng yao gen nin shuo zhe ge
zhi dao nin dui wo shuo gun kai
nin shi zai jie wan wo de hua hai shi zai dui wo shuo yi ci nei ge
zhi shi xiang zhi dao nin shi fou xu yao yi ge ding ji de mei ti ren
ha wo zhen de yi dian du bu xu yao ni
ni you xie guo shi le
ni jiu xiang shi kun zai guo qu de wei jing hai dao
wo you hen qiang de ren mai zhen de
hen gao ceng de ren xian sheng fei chang gao
huo xu ni neng gei wo lian luo shang ao si qia ying hou
hen hao xiao dan wo shi ren zhen de xian sheng
bu wo ye shi ren zhen de wo xiang gan ta
bu guan zen yang ni wei shi yao yao li kai ni he ni de lao er du qia zai fu zong tong de wu ka fei yin ka fei li le
bu wo men zhi shi du xu yao xin de tiao zhan
wo men shi yao zheng ge xiao zu du yao li kai
bu bu bu xian sheng qu ta ma de
ta yao tui xuan le bu wan quan bu shi
wo men ta ma de you xie yi wo liang nian hou dang xuan can yi yuan
liu nian hou wo men yi qi can jia da xuan
xie yi jiu shi zhe yang de ni ta ma wei shi yao bu zi sha
rang wo cheng qing yi xia xian sheng ru guo ta yao tui xuan de hua
nei yao ta ke neng da suan liu nian hou can xuan
er wo mei you zhen de shuo ta hui
e wo di cang tian xie xie ni ting xia lai
ni zhi dao ma ru guo wo zhi qian hai bu zhi dao
ni gong zuo zuo de you duo lan ni gang gang ye zheng ming le zhe yi dian
wo you xie zhong da de xiao xi nv shi
e wo you ju da de xiao xi
shi shi shang wo xiang ni bao zheng wo de xiao xi hui shi tou ban de nei zhong
er ni de da gai shi di liu ye yu le ban
de nei zhong wu liao xiao xi yu le jia zu qia dai shan
zong tong zhi dao zhe yi qie jiang ru he jie shu
suo yi ta he le wo nei yi lan se chao da ma ke bei
ha liang nian hou ta bu hui jing xuan lian ren le
bu wo shi ta ma de zhu ming xi ju yan yuan
wo dang ran shi ren zhen de
yi dan dang nei ling xiu fa xian ta bu hui can xuan
nei yao suo you dan he gou pi du hui yan xiao yun san
nei yao wei shi yao ta bu lai dui wo shuo wei shi yao shi ni gao su wo zhe ge
yin wei ta mei fa ren shou nei biao qing xiang nei ge
jiu xiang nei ge kong zhi bu zhu de xi yue
mo mo di ku qi
er zai ni de nao hai li ni zheng zai ta de mu shang tiao wu xuan zhuan
e bie gao su wo ni mei you wei ci gao xing
ni zhong yu neng bai tuo zhe li le
e bu shi gong zuo rang ren ju sang
sheng huo cai rang ren ju sang
bu wo ke yi wo neng zuo dao zhe ge
yin wei yi xie jin ji shi jian wo men xiang jian fu zong tong
bu xing cao ni de wo cong pian men jin
ni nei yao zuo de hua te qin ju te gong ke neng hui ning duan ni de bo zi
nei jiu bei ju le shi yao nv shi
e ni hao wo men neng tan tan ma
wo men dang ran neng tan tan hei neng qing ni gei wo suan nai ma
e zhe bie chi de tai kuai
e zhu zui da liang xiao guai de jia huo
hao le gei wo lai dian liu zhi de shi pin jia ba shao zi
ni xiang lai dian suan nai ma bu xie xie
ni kan qi lai bu cuo shun bian shuo e xie xie
shi yao ni zai duan lian hai shi shi yao
shi de wo yong lao de jiao lv liao fa xiao hao qia lu li
ni zhi dao de jiao lv
ru guo ni xiang zuo you yang yun dong ni de xian you xin cai xing a
wo ting shuo le yi ge hen zao gao de yao yan
shuo ni liang nian hou bu hui zai he zong tong yi qi jing xuan le
nei hen ling ren kun rao yin wei wo you dian xu yao
ni zai ci yi fu zong tong de shen fen can xuan
ran hou wo jin ru can yi yuan
ran hou ni he wo yi qi can xuan
ji zhu zhe shi xie yi shi de wo ji de nei ge
ni cong na ting lai de yao yan
e cong xiao jiang bing nei
you xiao hu zi de lie feng zui tong ming dian ying zhu jiao
shi yao ni zai kai wan xiao
shi xin xi wei di wang le ta ba
nei yao ni liang nian hou hui he zong tong yi qi jing xuan
liang nian hou wo jue dui hui can xuan
nei zhi hou de si nian jing xuan lian ren bao bei
ni shuo jing xuan lian ren shi shi yao yi si
bu shi jing xuan lian ren nei ge shi hou shi jing xuan
shi de mei cuo ni he wo jing xuan
deng deng dan ni gang gang wei shi yao shuo jing xuan lian ren
shi yao ni shuo le jing xuan lian ren
nei jiu yi wei zhao you shi yao qi ta de shi qing fa sheng le
wo zhi de shi can xuan ni zhi dao wo shuo de shi shi yao

zhe jiu xiang shuo yi ran de he rong yi ran shao de
du shi yi yang de yi si wo wen dao le you mao ni de wei dao
e bi zui wo ye gao su ni nei shi shi yao yi si

zou xiao qi de ji lao zou le
hao ba wo qin ai de fu zong tong ban zi zai na
zhe you yi ge wo xu yao wo de fu zong tong ban zi

ni xi huan zuo ai he lv you

wo you hua yao shuo

wo bu hui li kai zong tong hui li kai
ta bu hui jing xuan lian ren le
wo hui can xuan e tian na
wo hui jing xuan zong tong e ye
tai bang le wo wan quan mei xiang dao a
ta dian ran le ta men peng
peng wo men zhe shi yao shang tian le
wo zhi qian li zhu zai wo de chuan shang yi jing zhe yao jin le
e tian na wo zhi gong xi nv shi
he wo de he xin dui wu dai yi hui ma

ni bu zai li mian

wo zai ni de tou shang kan dao le yi ge deng pao ding

ni men bu xu yao zhao qi ta gong zuo le
ni men zai zhe he wo yi qi

o ni hui ju diao ta men de dui ba

wo hui qu he zuo sheng yi

 wo xiang qi ta ren ye hui zhe yao shuo

nei yao zai wei lai de yi san ge yue li
wo men jiu hui yi zhi wan shui shi yao shi hou zhi dao le shi yao shi

zao huo ji men zao
yi san ling ling ling bu shi yi si wu ling ling
nei shi ni jin tian dui jing zi kua de ci shu ma
bu wo zhi shi zai cai xin shui de cha bie

wo zhi dao ni you yi ge mian shi

que bao ni you zheng que de di zhi

wo jiu le jie le ni xiang fa
er qie ma ma xi huan
bao qian ma ma xi huan nei ge
wo hen bao qian dui bu qi jiu yi hui
wo bu zhi dao wo de mi ma shi shi yao ni zhi dao
zhe shi si ni bu xu yao wu xian wang luo nv shi dan biao zhi du zai zhe
ni xu yao zuo de jiu shi guan diao wu xian wang luo
nei jiu hui po shi ta zhuan xiang si ni zhi dao wo shi dui de
hao ba bie nei yao zuo wo bu que ding zen yao zuo
bu bu bu nei shi ji mi de wo bu hui peng ren he dong xi
wo bu hui peng ren he dong xi a wo gang kai shi le yi chang he yi lang de zhan zheng
wan xiao ta yi dian du bu hao xiao
nei zhi shi wo de jing dian xiao hua zhi yi
qiang wu zei he xi hu lu e nei shi gei zhe wei de
hao de gei ye xu lai dian gan lan
e bie bie bie bie chu qu
hao ba wo men de ou zhou fang wen
gang gang bian cheng tong wang di yu de dan xiang lv cheng ran hou hui lai
shi shi shang nei shi ge hui cheng ni zhi dao ma
jiu liang miao zhong ni neng bu neng bi shang zui
wo men wei shi yao bu zou mei cuo wo men de ti qian jie shu zhe ci wu can le
dan shi ni zhi dao ni hui yong jiu chi you ni de bao suo yi guan ta ma de
xia wu hao xian sheng men
tong ji meng zai ci ke kai shi
jin tian jiu shi shi fa dian
zhe jiu shi mei guo zhi shu
ta hui rang wo men le jie ren men jiang ru he tou piao
shen zhi zai ta men zi ji yi shi dao zhi qian
zhe ge xiang mu dian fu le
wo men guan yu zi ji shi ru he si kao de xiang fa
yi ge xiao shi qian de guo zong li
biao da le ta dui zhe zhong ping lun de shi wang
ta yi wei ta shi na gen cong
shi jie bao fa guo bao zhi de qiao zhi dan ni si
cheng fu zong tong shi yi dian xing de mei guo tu bao zi
wo ren wei fa yin shi ni
wo bu shi tu bao zi qu ni de de pa er di e fa guo ying xing da bi zi qing sheng
wo ren wei nei shang le he
ran hou jiu cong nei shang mian bao fa le
wu nei xie ci ting qi lai ji qi er shu
wo zhi shi chao xi huan nei shou ge
ran hou wo cai ni xiang ba ta chuan bo chu qu
suo yi wo jiu ba ta fang nei le
gei wo gun xia fei ji
gun xia qu nv shi wo men zheng zai hua xing zhong
wo ren zhen de ni ma de gei wo gun xia qu
 ta ma de gei wo gun xia qu
wo wu fa xiang xin ni ju ran ba nei ge fang dao shang mian le
xi huo wo men neng rang xia qu yao ma fan
ni suo you de te quan du jiang bei bo duo
hao ba dan bu bao kuo ting che wei mei cuo ting che wei
deng deng shi yao ni you ting che wei xian zai mei you le
shi de xian zai mei le dan wo shen zhi hai mei you mai che
wo gang qian le yi liang ri chan liang nian de zu yue
rang ta xia qu hao ba huo ji men wo de bao zai xing li jia shang
ta you ge da bao bao ma
hao le hao duo le
du hao le quan hao le
wo hen hao shi fen hao
zhe ci hang cheng you duo jiu
shu zi ta men cong bu jie shu dui yao
dan nei jiu shi ta men de you dian
ta men hui yi zhi ji xu xia qu
ta ying gai bei zi sha jian kong
mei cuo que bao ta ting guo qu
nei shi la ding yi xuan piao dui ba
lai wo ban gong shi shi xian sheng
wo ji tian qian cong ni zhe zu le yi liang ri chan
ru guo wo bu zai xu yao ta wo you na xie xuan ze
wo neng ba ta tui hui qu yao
bang bang shi you ting
bie gao feng hua er jie
bu yao ti qi yi se lie
ge wei zi you mei ti de qing lian hu min guan gu luo ma guan zhi
qing xiang yong zhe xie fen lan shi zao can
zheng ru ni men suo zhi fu zong tong zui jin yu fen lan qian shu le
yi xiang shi fen ju you li shi yi yi de ruan jian he zuo xie yi
ta de ou zhou fang wen shi fou bei nei shou ge de yin ying long zhao
ni zhi dao de jiu shi nei shou ta chao xiao ou zhou ren de ge
ta mei you chao xiao ou zhou ren
wo hui shuo nei shou ge hen gao xiao gao xiao
dan geng zhong yao de shi xian zai fu zong tong
zheng yu guo hui duo shu dang ling xiu hui wu
ta men zheng zai xie shang yi xiang
neng bi mian zheng fu ting gong de zhai wu xue jian
jiang cheng wei mei guo shi shang
zui you xiao lv de fu zong tong zhi yi
zai jie jiu wu zi bie ke si tan ren zhi shi jian zhong ta qi le guan jian xing de zuo yong
ta zhi dao qi zhong yi ge ren zhi shi jian die
er shi de qi ta san ge xue sheng de sheng ming shou dao le wei xie ma
huo xu dang shi bu shi hen qing chu
nei yao ta nei xie shuo ta zi ji zai zhe ci jun shi jie jiu xing dong zhong
ban yan le zhong yao jiao se de hua du shi huang yan ge
hao ba man yi dian ni de xie tang tai di le ma
bu ru lai dian dian xin huo zhe fei yu zen yao yang
qing hui da wen ti wo bu zhi dao ta zhi dao shi yao
huo zhe ta shi he shi zhi dao de
yao yao ta zhi dao nei ge xue sheng shi ge jian die
ran hou zai fou ren zhe jian shi de shi hou sa le huang
yao yao ta bu zhi dao ta shi jian die
dan shi huang cheng zi ji zhi dao zhe ci jun shi jie jiu xing dong de xi jie
zhe bu shi you yi ci shuo huang zhe shi jian
e xian zai shi le
zhe bu shi ge rong yi shi er
e zhe shi jian nan de xie yi tan pan
ni bu dan xin ma wo zhi dao ru he tao jia hai jia
ni er zi hai hao ma ta men hen bu cuo
ni ta er yi le

ta men kuai le jian kang mei cuo

wo hen liang ya ni ju ran neng na nei ge kai wan xiao

ni bei ci ji le bi shang ni de chou zui

wo zuo bu lai zou ba bu
wo mei fa zai zhe zhong zao yin xia zuo suan shu
wo wu fa ren shou xiao gu niang le ni mei dang guo xiao gu niang yao
cong bu wo ye mei you
wei fu zong tong gong zuo de he
gun kai mei wen ti
hei jin wan fu zong tong kan qi lai hen xing gan
wo hao qi yao duo shao bei fu te jia xia du
wo men cai neng yi du luo bin xun fu ren feng cai can jian dian ying bi ye sheng
zhe tai bu zun zhong le
ni zai shuo shi yao
zhe shi zui gao zan yu le hao yao
wo xi huan ni men zai yi qi gei zao cheng de ju da bu shuang
he yi qian yue hui guo shun bian shuo
e xie xie zhe ge bei jing jie shuo
nei shi bu shi shuo ni zhong hui shi chang le
bao qian ni zhe shi bu shi zai wo yue hui de shi hou diao wo ma zi
ni you chi yao ma
shi de kang sheng su bao chi huo li
wo jing shen mei you wen ti
ru guo ni shi zai an shi zhe ge de hua
e hei da jia hao
da jia hao wo jiu shi xiang
dui wo le bu qi de nv er shuo ji ju hua
ni zhi dao de wo xiang ting xia lai ran hou shuo
wo ren wei zai zhe yang de shi hou
neng he jia ren he peng you jian mian zhen shi bang ji le
neng qing ting jia ren he peng you
neng su shuo he qing ting
hai you jiang hua he you ren ling ting
wo ren wei you shi wo men zhi shi xu yao hua xie shi jian
bu yong tai chang wo de yi si shi da gai shi fen zhong huo
e huo zhe shi wu fen zhong ye bu cuo
wo jian yi wo men lai dian you jian she xing de tan hua shi jian
nei yao ni men you shi yao an jing xie de yin le ma
ran hou ni men ke yi yi zhi bo fang zhi dao
zhi dao kan xiang wo wo gei ni men xin hao
bu shi zai nei zhi qian mei wen ti
e hai you sheng ri kuai le
hao ba ru guo zai shi ye fu li shang ni neng gei wo yi
e wo ke yi tong yi quan guo wei sheng yan jiu suo jian yi ling
nong ye bu tie shang jian ba
di xian shi ni qu nian de yu suan ti an
dui de hao ba hao ba nei xie shu zi jia qi lai
wo jia chu lai shi yi ling yi er
yi er ni zen yao de dao de
ni wang le neng yuan dang ran
kan kan zhe ge nei yao wo men da cheng yi zhi le
e mei cuo bang ji le
shi de wo men da cheng yi zhi le mei cuo
zhe tiao jian zhen kuai sha le wo le dan wo men da cheng yi zhi le wan cheng le
wan cheng le gong xi
wo wu fa xiang xin zhe bu shi
wo wu fa xiang xin zhe bang ji le
hen hao xian zai wo de shuo fu wo de dang tuan le
zai wo bian hui nan gua zhi qian ni hui cheng gong de
mei cuo e shang di
tian na er yi sui de ren zou de zhen kuai
shi a wo zao zhi dao le
nin kan qi lai bu cuo nv shi
e xie xie ni zhen de kan qi lai hen bang
xie xie shi de nv shi
ni men kan guo zhe ge le ma
qie dan gao he bin ke men chang sheng ri kuai le ge de shi hou
fu zong tong wu chu ke xun
ta men shuo wo he chao fan le
wo men de guan xi shi chang pian ju
zhe bang qin shou xian shi dai an nuo wang fei xian zai shi zhe ge
ta men ren wei yi kai shi
ni he shi dui zhao jing tou zuo xi
ta men zai ci wan qi le shuo huang zhe de lan geng
hei shui ba nei ge wa chu lai de
bu zhi dao ye xu shi mou xie ji zhu ta de chun huo
ran hou tu ran bei da si zhui peng
xian zai shi lai zi he fen dun you bao
ji jiang chu ban de shu xuan cheng
nin he zai zong tong xuan zhan shi de guan xi
shi ni shuo de yong lai mi huo xuan min de huang yan
nei shi ge huang yan dui ba
mei cuo nei shi shi shi bing qie que shi fa sheng le dan nei shi sa de huang
bu shi wo mei cuo
shuo huang zhe xian zai ke shi da re dian
ni zhi dao de jiu xiang ren men shuo de ru guo ya yun jiu hui gong ming
shui shuo de mei ren nei yao shuo
wo hen que ding you ting ren shuo guo
e xian zai bian cheng xu shu yu qi le
shuo de shi ni yi qian jia zhuang le
xian zai ken ding ye shi zhuang chu lai de
e bang ji le lv lai le xiao xiong wei ni li de you yu lv
xie yi peng pai dui peng
ni jiu shi peng peng fu zong tong
e hen fan gan zuo wan zai pai dui shang tan cai zheng de bu su zhi ke
jin wan he wo de dai ta qu chi wan fan
lai mi bu zuo tian de pai dui suo yi
hao ba nei hui mian xiang gong zhong
suo yi bu guan ni zai zuo shi yao bie kan qi lai xiang zai nong xu zuo jia
yin wei shuo huang zhe yi jing bian cheng le ta niang de da xue beng le
shi de hai yong ni shuo wo xian zai jiu zai xue beng li chang you
hai shi tong guo hu xi guan hu xi de
ni de fa biao yi fen sheng ming hao ma
wo de si sheng huo shi yin si shi de
hai you he wo wo men xiang chu de hai hao
wo men shi shi shang xiang chu de shi hai bu cuo
zhe hen hao zhuang de hen xiang
bu zhe bu shi zhuang de zhe shi zhen de
e hao ba bang ji le jiu nei yao shuo
zuo wan de pai dui
bian cheng le yi ge jing ji feng hui
dan shi ni zhi dao ma wo men jin wan wei le ni er xiang ju
sheng ri kuai le hai you ni
he sha yu tong you de nan ren
hai kai shi zi you qian shui le zhen de ma nei shi shi yao
shi bu shi nei zhong jin li bie qi bie dao di de
jiu xiang gan en jie wan can hou zuo zai wo ma pang bian nei yang
ma ma ni you kai shi jia xiao le
shi yao hei zhe hen hao
wo du kan bu chu lai shi jia xiao
ni cong lai du bu zhi dao wo shi bu shi zhuang de san su shuang guan
wu  ni shi shi yao mou zhong zhuan jia
zai mou xie ling yu ba
xian zai zhe shi gan shi yao zhe shi diao qing
ni ma ma shi ge chu se de diao qing zhe
ni de zuo xie diao qing bi ji
zhe bu shi diao qing
zhe jiu he zai shang fang luo zhao yi yang zhi bai
hui zhu yi dao zhe ge yin xing ren ma
lai zi bo shi dun zheng zhi xing dong wei yuan hui ban gong shi de
ni jue de ru guo wo chuan shang zheng zhi xing dong wei yuan hui zhi fu de hua
wo zhi dao bao qian
bao qian bu guo ni wei shi yao yao bao qian
wo ting dao lao sao suo yi wo yi wei wo xu yao dao qian
ni you duo chang shi jian mei you ting wo shuo hua le
wo zhi shi hen xu yao mi qie guan zhu zhe ge
yin wei jiu xiang yi zuo xiu mian huo shan
ke neng sui shi bao fa
wo xiang wo yao chi xie shan bei
wo xiang wo yao chi wo zhi dao ni xiang yao chi shi yao
ni yao chi bie nei yao zuo
wu ba ni de shou fang xia lai
wo mei fa ren shou zhe zhong nan ren zhi shang shi de ao man
wo zhen de mei fa ren shou
hao ba nei bu shi ao man
qu ni ma de ni nei yao xiang
yuan liang wo wo zhi shi zai yu ce ni de dian can
shi shi yao yang pai
shi de wo hen bao qian wo le jie ni
yuan liang wo ni dui wo er yan bu shi ge da mi ti
er wo fei chang xiang shou zhe zhong xiang da le shi gao de jiang ying xiao rong
jia zhuang yi qie du hen hao yin wei ren men zai kan zhao
bie zhe yao hun dan
ni de zuo chu tong yang de lian
ni ye de zhe yao xiao jiu shi zhe yang
hao ba e xian zai zhe zhong diao qing suan shi bi jiao yin hui le
ni ren shi shui ni zhi dao ma
shi de ta shi hen hao de ren
wo men du hen xi huan ba ling nian dai de you qing xi ju
hen feng ci de shi zhe jiu shi wo men bian cheng peng you de fang shi
ni wei shi yao zai zhe
ni zhen de mei you ren he shi ke yi zuo shi ma
qiao bie li ta bie li shui
hei wo jue de zhe li de nei wei nv shi gang gang pai le
wo ming bai ni men zhi jian shi ai hen jiao zhi
dan hen duo ren de zhe xie gan qing du hui lun zhao lai
ta men bu hui tong shi zhan lu ai hen liang zhong qing xu
wo men yi zhi bao chi zhao fan fu wu chang de guan xi
ni zhe yao shuo zhi de shi feng dao diao zha ba
ji qing zong shi dang zhong bu ke que shao de bu fen mei cuo

zhi hou shi man chang er xin ku de
hao ba wo jue de ni men ma shang jiu yao
zai zhe zhang zhuo shang kai gan le er nei zhen de hui hui diao wo de sheng ri

wo shi shuo wo men shi xing ai de dong wu dang ran e tian na
wo men you guo xing ai wo men ni zhi dao
wo shi shuo hen bang de xing ai hen bang de xing ai
hao ba wo de gei wo de xin li yi sheng fa duan xin le
nei ge bu neng he jiu shi zen yao hui shi
wo shi ge gui ge jiao tu shi yao
che dan mei ren shi ta ma de gui ge jiao tu
ni da gai ren wei bao chi leng jing hui rang ni bao chi zhuang tai
e cai wo nu li gong zuo ye nu li wan jian ren
zhe shi wo de xin tiao
wo ba gai si de nei ge wen zai le wo de shang hai you kong yu de di fang
ni shen zhi du hai bu shi ren
ni zhi neng suan shi ren de cao gao
nei cao gao shang zhi sui bian hua le yi ge ju da de gu jia
ke ta men mei you shi jian qu tian jia xi jie
bi fang shuo shang se la zi zun la zhi lei de dong xi
ru guo ke xue guai ren shi yong si ren de lao er pin qi lai de hua can jian tong ming ke huan xiao shuo ji dian ying
ni jiu shi nei ge guai wu
wo qu xi shou jian
bie zai wo li kai de shi hou rang ni men zi ji nan kan
wo men hui jin liang shi shi
hen gao xing jian dao ni
wo neng da rao yi hui ma wu bu xing
kan qi lai zhe you hen duo ren zheng zai fa tui te
hai you zhao xiang suo yi ni men da gai xi wang neng zhu yi xia zi shi
hai hao xie xie ni ke yi li kai le
hao de shi de hao ba
wo xiang gao su ni dian shi
wu gong guan fu ze ren gao su wo

wo xian bei peng shang le tian
ran hou bei hen hen di shuai dao le di shang
wo wu fa xiang xin ni gang gang gao su wo de shi qing
ni zhi dao wei xiao
wei xiao ni zhe yu chun de hun dan xiao kai yi dian
ni zhi dao mei ti xian zai shi zen yao zhong kou yi ci shuo wo de yao
ta men hui zen yao yang bao dao
wo zi zhu wo dui shou de gu shi
ni jiu shi ge ta ma de chun huo
wo bu hui nei yao shuo
hao ba xian zai fa sheng le shi yao
ni men kan qi lai jiu xiang yao yong niu pai dao tong dui fang
wo men zheng zai chao jia wo men ye zai wei xiao
ran hou bai chu xu jia de biao qing ni ye neng zuo dao jiu shi zhe yang
zhe zhi shi sheng yi
wo men xi wang zui zhong neng he sheng li zhe yi qi
mei you ren he si ren en yuan zai li mian wo bao zheng
wo shen zhi bu zhi dao zhe jian shi
e che ni ma de dan
dan ni zhi dao ma wo hui gao ding ta
wo que shi hui zhe xie du hen hao
wo men neng bao chi wei xiao bao chi wei xiao mei cuo
wo xiang ru guo ni men ji xu wei xiao
ni men hui de yong jiu xing de ya guan jin bi zheng
bu shi ma zhen feng ci
wo hen bao qian da rao ni men wo gang jie dao de dian hua
e lai gong xi wo yin wei wo cu cheng le zuo wan de xie yi
mei guo gan xie ni bu ke qi
zong tong hui zan huan nei ge xie yi

dan bu shi xian zai

wo de deng yi hui

ni zai gan shi yao e

wo di cang tian a gei ni
hu luo bu dan gao hen bu cuo
ni yao shi shi ma bu yao
wo neng yong shou ji lai qie ta

che bu cuo a xin che yao

wo qian le shi wan kuai

ni xian zai shi zui le yao
zao shang hao xian sheng ni kan mei kan nei pian di yu zhu yi de wen zhang

o ta zai zhe ni ni hao a

hai you ge xiao xie de

cong na gan hui lai dui bu qi wo ba si wu you ge hui

shi yao bu e nv shi

ni zai zhong qi xuan ju hou da ying zong tong shuo de
ni zhi dao ma ni neng bu neng chuan shang pao xie
ran hou ta ma gan jin gei wo pao dao zhong dian
jin tian bei qia luo zhou de zhu rou wei yuan hui you xuan zhu bi sai

zong tong xi wang ni neng chu xi

zheng shi zai xia nv shi
hao ba ta men xiang rang wo qu zhu rou shao kao hui shang
jian yi qun ke neng hui zai kao zhu zhi qian
lun liu gan nei tou zhu de ren yao
wo jue de ta men bu hui lun liu de

jiu suan wo yao rang xiang chao ren nei yang
fan zhao rao di qiu fei yi quan rang shi jian dao liu
ni ming bai ma shi de nv shi

wo xiang zhe ge xuan zhu bi sai shi ge hen hao de ji hui
o shi de ni bu yong qu le qu pei ni ba ba
wo hui gei ni dai san ming zhi hai you liu zhi lao gong hui lai de

xie tian xie di a
wo men de zou le zan men de qu gen xiang ba lao men da cheng yi pian le
zhong yi yuan da guo dian hua lai ta xi wang he nin mian tan
hao ba wo xiang yi xia nei wo ning ke zai wo de mu er shang dian yi ba huo
yi si jiu shi bu gan ta xian zai si chu ban hao ren

o nv shi zen yao le o bu yao a
wo yao zou le wo yao gen nin yi qi qu
shi yao zong tong xi wang wo qu jian ce mei guo hei
yin wei shi wo de bao bei xiang mu o wo lei ge cang tian a
zhe ken ding shi ni di yi ge mei you dong yong ma zui yao
gao lai de bao bei xiang mu
shi de nei du shi yi qian de shi le
ni neng chu li de shi yao
wo you di fang yao qu na a
e wo xiang wo zhao dao jie jin de ban fa le
ru guo ni yao sha le ta niang ran hou chuan ta de pi de hua nei yan ge lai shuo ke shi fan fa de yo
fu zong tong ban gong shi xian zai zheng wei
xin wai jiao zheng ce mo quan ca zhang ni xian sheng
wo gang kan le yi pian hen you yi si de wen zhang
shuo wei shi yao di yu zhu yi shi bi guo jia zhu yi
geng jia jian shi de zheng zhi ji chu
ni shi bu shi gang jia ru zhe jia pu la ti ban a xian sheng
shi de zhe li hen fang bian
ni zhu na fu jin
jiu shi zhe yi pian
wo ting shuo ren zhi de shi yu yan yu lie le
xi wang ni yi qian zuo guo pu la ti
ren men zong yi wei zi ji sui bian jiu neng shang zhe xie ji qi
bu wo lian le liu ge yue cai kai shi yong zhe ge de
shi a wo yong yuan du zhao yan chang yuan mu biao
wo zai kong jun er hao he ka fei yo

e wo xian zai bu xu yao he jiang jun tan hua
ta hen ji qie wo xian zai bu xu yao ta de dian hua
e jiang jun zai xian shang
ni neng shao deng yi hui ma
jiang jun wo hen bao qian wo de da zhe tong dian hua fu zong tong nv shi
dan wo men zheng zhun bei
zai er wu fen zhong hou tao lun ren zhi qing kuang
ni jue de ni neng gan dao hai shi wo men gai zai ni que xi de qing kuang xia zhi jie tao lun
bu bu bu bie zai wo dao zhi qian jin xing
wo men ke yi zai fei ji li zuo shi pin lian xian wo qu chu li mei wen ti
nei yao nei yang ying gai ke yi hen wan mei di jie jue wen ti
wo xi wang neng liu xia lai wo de wu wu
dai zai zhe ni ye yi yang shi de hao ba
xie xie fu zong tong nv shi xie xie
shi shi shang wo men huo xu gai zou le
wo de hui qu wei qi zhong kao shi xue xi le
shi de shi de ni fu mu de ming zi shi
nei ge kan qi lai shi ge bu cuo de nan hai shi de nv shi
gei ta he ta de quan jia zuo yi ge an quan jian cha

e ni da suan wen wo yao qian ma
wo mei zhe yao xiang bu bu bu

ni jue de zhe yang mei wen ti yao
shi de bu bu bu xing
wo mei fa xiang zhe yang jin xing shi pin hui yi
wo ya gen mei fa bai tuo zhe ge ya hen

e ni you chui feng ji ma mei you

ye shi de zhu yi bu shi

xiang ta de mou ge nv peng you

wo bu xiang zhe yao shuo

wo du guo le zui hao de yi tian
zhen shi yi duan mei hao de shi guang
wo men zai kong jun er hao shang mei guo hei zheng shi kai shi le

ni men xiang wan yi xia de pin zi you xi ma

hei hai lai zhe ma
bu ta li kai le

wo gei ni de ming zi she ding le gu ge jing bao
e ni kan le you bao shang
guan yu ren zhi qing kuang de wen zhang yao
ni shi nei ge zong shi zai ting che ku li xiang wo wen hao de ren ma
e wo de qu ju yi hui ta ma de ya ling
zhe shi gei chi dun de chun huo men yong de
wei shen me bu neng jin wu chen

ni dui shei hao wo zhen de

hao xiang zhui ju a xian zai

wo men dao di zai qi dai shen me
wo jiu ba mai de dong xi

hei ma pi jing men hao

e xuan wo zhong zu he xie kua yue hong gou
nei jiu shi bing gan he nai you
o qu ni ma de bu bu shi shuo ni xian sheng
dui yu rong chang bian lun gai ge fa an wo hen xing fen
ting dao zhe ge zhen gao xing
ru guo ni neng na dao can yi yuan gai liang fa an
jiu dai biao ta de que xu yao gai
zhe shi liang ren de dui
wo shi zhi zhe jiu xiang
quan fu yi ge ren da zi ji yi quan
gao su wo xian sheng

zhe shi ge wei miao de qu yu
ni gen shi you chan ye bu shi yi bian de ma

zai qu yao fang de lu shang wo jiu bao fa le
zhe shi wo dan xin de

ni mei shuo hao ba mei
wo shuo de shi 
shi zhe yang wo men dui shi you chan ye shuo ke yi rang ta men cha yi jiao
suo yi wo men cai neng zai nei tiao can ju wei bo shang quan shen er tui
wo zhi dao zhi dao
ta zhi dao wo zhi shi bei mi zhu le

ni dang shi zai na

o tai bang le shi

wo yao qu tou qi
wo men dai hui yao tan tan

 bu hui bu xing ma

wo zhen xin xi wang ni shi di yi ge zhi dao de

wo bei ge chu rong chang bian lun de shi fan de yao si lian liao tian du ji mei le
zhou chang hen gao xing jian dao ni lao you

ni dui wo mei shi mo jian she xing de jian yi ma
guan yu lv se chan ye de ma
o jia le lia gao shi you de hai neng zhe mo jiao ma
wa ni men yao mai duo shao pen qi cai neng gei nei tuo dai xie wu bao jin yi a
ren ren you qi quan li fan wei can yi yuan ji shi shi fu zong tong
dui er wo you quan che li
zhe ye zheng shi wo xian zai yao zuo de
ta shuo de che li ta ta bu shi zhi
che li ge chu rong chang bian lun gong zuo dui ba
wei ta zai shuo shi mo
wo yi wei shi zhi ta yao che li tan hua
chu le tian zhu jiao tu he guan jia shui hui ba che li dang dong ci yong
yi se lie jun fang ou er yong
wei wo bu zhi dao a ni shao shua
kuai zou wo men hui
bu bu bu xing wo yao liu
yao ban gong ke yi yong wang luo dui ba zhi bian ge
xie xie fei chang gan xie
wo men you gong zuo
chan ye ge chu rong chang bian lun
zhi dao wo men xu yao shi mo ma geng xun chang geng qin min de hua
wo you ge zhu yi
ni ke yi tan tan ju guang deng xia ni de shang chun duo mo shui run
zhan xian ni de xun chang
wo shuo de jue dui shi wan quan bu tong de xun chang
zui hou yi xian liao jie wei dui ba
shi hong ren dui de fen
xu hui ti qi gan lan
wu ya dui qiu mi suo yi
fu zong tong nv shi ni de wu ya dui jin nian biao xian ru he
wo jia wu ya chao zan zhi dao yuan yin ma
yin wei wo men you zuo si fen wei zhu ming qiu xing sui nian qing dan zhan ji fei ran
hong ren dui jin nian de kuai gong da fa hen bu cuo
shuo shi hua ni men nei ge wai jie yuan
dui ni men ke mei sha hao chu
hao ba wo zen mo ke neng ji de zhu
yi pi jiu de ming yi fa shi wu ya tie ding ying
ke yi tan tan nei ge
guan yu ta zen mo rang ni fu zhang de pi jiu
ta you mei you zuo zhe ge dong zuo rang ni bu zhi dao shi gai bao ta hai shi ba ta ding shang shi zi jia
shun bian yi ti wo shi xiang ding ta shi zi jia de
liu xia ting ta de yan
qi kai de sheng ling you tong ming de gan lan qiu ji lu dian ying
rang wo si le ta
bu shi gai shao le zhe tuan gou sheng
bie bie xian deng deng ta zai fei ye gei ni liu le ji ju
ju ran xie cheng le yang mu ni de tong dao
zhen shi ge hun dan
dui hua sheng dun chu pin de gou
wo zhen shi fan si le hei wo
wo shi shuo tong dao ta xian ran shi zai kai wan xiao dui ba
ta bu hui zhen de yi wei ta you neng li
sheng ren fu zong tong jing xuan ren ba
wu mei li bu fan de zhan zheng ying xiong
dui dan wo shi shuo zong tong
zong shi hui zhi chi xian ren fu zong tong ba
er qie ta bu hui rang xuan ze ni bian cheng tian da de shi wu
nei ke zhen ke ai
wo tao lao le ni shi bu shi zhe ge yi si
wo shi zhi hao de tao lao jiu xiang wei xi hun yin shi mo de
bu hui pao qi ni
jing dian xing bu zen mo
wo pai shou ji de qing bao ma jian yu zhe xie feng sheng
bie rang ta zhi dao ni dan xin le bie dang ta shi hui shi
bie dang ta shi hui shi hao ma
bu guo tang ruo da shi guo zhen ru ci
nei wo que shi xu yao zao zuo zhun bei bi ru
shou ji qing bao shi mo de
zhi dao wo zui fan shi mo ma
ke neng ba mou ren jiu chu qi huo tan ke de chun gu shi
bai tuo wei shi mo jun ren xing ying jin yi wu du neng de jiang zhang
nei jia huo yi ran yan zhong shao shang le jiu suan zhen shi ye bu gou ji shi
wei wei ni de zhuo zi zai hou mian
suo yi wo zheng yong
qing gao su ta qin quan gui ze hao ma
de wo shi you er yuan lao shi ma
e bu ni bu shi hao ba sui ni bian
yong ni hou mian de zhuo
mo yong pei can tai
kan shui lai le huo ji men ni men zui ai de yo
ni du bu shi ni ma de zui ai
bie gai hui jian xin wen jie de tan hua yao dian hao ma wo gang zhun bei hao
wo shi lai chuan da zong tong de xie wei yao qiu de
ta xiang yong yao kong qi zhi hui wo ma
bu nei zai ke ji shang bu ke neng
e zong tong xi wang ni bu yao guo fen qiang diao ge chu rong chang bian lun
ni shuo shi mo ni nei shi wo zui ju dai biao xing de fu zong tong gai ge xing dong
ben ren qi jin zhuan zhu yu jing ji
qu shou shi dong xi
hai you jian shi zhe xie gai jia shui le
zong tong geng xi wang ni xuan ze yi min fa an
mei guo gong min bei fei fa yi min qiang zou gong zuo zhu ru ci lei
wo zheng ge chu qi jing xuan du shi wei yi min te she shuo hua
ni zhen yi wei you ren ji de ni de chu qi jing xuan ma
chu le kai tou ban ju wo mei cha jue dao
sheng xia de wen ti zhong you yi si zun zhong
wo de chu zhong shi dan hua xuan qu de hui yi
er fei gong jie ni de jing xuan xiao neng
nei wei shi mo ni bu zhi jie nei mo shuo ni
o yin wei ni de she jiao neng li shi lang jiao de
o hai you ba zhong guo qiang diao cheng mao yi huo ban
wo men bi xu jian chi qiang diao zhe dian
wo gai hui bai gong qu le tian a wo zhen xi huan zhe shuo fa
ta zhen shi ge hao ren
dan ta zhen de rang wo che di ru suan le
hai you qiang diao zhong guo
nei suan shi dui de ci tan ma
hao ba wo xiang wo men hui bu le jia le
zhou ri zao qi si wu fu zong tong guan di
wan shang wan de kai xin ma
wo de la lian huai le
wo bu de bu kai che dao chu zhao xiu li ti huan
wo zen mo guo de wo wan shang qi dian shang
wan shang qi dian hai shi zhou liu wan li huan nve ji de ren du shui de bi nei wan
ta men shui bu zhao de yin wei ke sou
hai huo ji men wo zhun bei hao le ma shang xia lai
wo gai zou le zhi yu ni ma
xiang dai duo jiu dai duo jiu wo wan shi gei ni da dian hua hao ma
neng he ni yi qi zou ma
wo bu xiang ta men kan dao
e wai gui cheng zhen shi tai guai
dao dan wo ke shi fu zong
o dui ni dang ran shi

o wo de que shi fu zong tong
o bao bei wo zhun bei chi wu can le
wo zhun bei chi ni le
o zao shang di er hui mei xiang dao ni you zhe neng nai ni
o lao tian wo zhen xiang shui ru jiao rong
wo yao hao hao xin shang ni de qiao tun
hao le du dai qi le
liu wan guo de ru he

ni zen mo zhe mo lei de yang zi ni sha du mei gan
zhe shi dui de diao cha
zhu yi di yi ye

zhen shi ge hao xiao
jian xin wen jie hai you geng duo hao xiao
wo yao ba ta chi gan mo jing le
ti yu hua ti jiu yao gai bian
wo men zhi xu ba hong ren gai cheng zhi chi de qiu dui
zhi chi na ge dui
xin ta shi zhi jia ge xiong de fen
ni que xin nei ke bang bu shang
mei guan xi ni yao liao de shi wu ya dui
wo zhi dao wo shi wu ya qiu mi
dan wan yi ye shi wu ya qiu mi ni ni ming bai ma
dui wu ke wan bu qi lai dui ba
you xi li jiu ke
you ren shuo ni de yi min zheng ce
qu jue yu ni de jiu ye ji hua
ni zen mo hui ying

wo qiang lie xiang xin
ni jin tian mei you zen mo ti dao can yi yuan ge chu rong chang bian lun ji hua

jiu yao you suo xing dong
hua ti yin dao rong chang bian lun le
nan xing wai sheng zhi qi zeng da zhen

ta xian zai shuo de ke shi ge chu rong chang bian lun
ta zi ji wen ta de
wo de yi xiang hen jian dan wo de yi xiang jiu shi tong yi
wo de wen ni yi xia ni shi xiong dui qiu mi
le ti yu hua ti mei
wo men yi dian ye bu dan xin you wan shi an yi
wo du ping pi jiu wo men chu di de fen ying de bi sai
nei ta de you shi ye hen da yu tong wei wu ya dui yuan
zhe ge ta e ta da de bu cuo
wo men xia zhou zai jian
yin wei mei feng zhou ri hui jian xin wen jie
ni hui kan de mian dui quan guo jie mu ma
bu guo wo hai you pai ju suo yi wo kong pa de tiao guo
guan chang qi huan cheng gong lu zi jin hen you zong tong qian
nei wo hui hen chi liang de yan ge shuo lai ta bu suan mei guo ren

de yin wei ta de fu mu

he lu yin shi tan tan ma

wo bu ke yi xiao ti da zuo

cong xiao lian bian cheng le ku gua

wo mei ting dao ren he wen ti

wo tong yi wo tong yi

ken ding shi chuan yang kai lai le

wo gai zen mo ban

o gan xie shen a tai ke pa le

o zhe shen hen chen ni

hao ba wo cai wo men ying fu de bu cuo
gang gang zheng shi mu qian er ren yu nan er si ren shou shang
wo bu shi nei ge yi si wo men de qu tang yi yuan
ni you mei you neng huan de zheng zhuang
ni you mei you bu shi sheng dan lao ren fu

ke bu shi wan sheng jie yao tang guo

dan bu guan zen yang ye shi yi xiang te quan
nv shi wo bu zhi dao zhe xie ren shi bu shi du huo zhao
ni jiu zheng chang liao tian jiu hao le hao ma
liao tian liao shi mo liao tian qi ma
bu guo xian zai que shi shi fan ji jie gao wen tian qi shi ba

 zen mo an pai du xing

wo lai wo wo ni de shou

 wo de xuan min yi jing yan juan le

wo jue de ta bu shi he zai ban gong shi chuan
wo zhi shi lai kan kan he zhou chang zhi jie de wu hui jie chu mei
shi a yi qie du hao hao ji le hao de bu neng zai hao le
hen hao nei wo hui qu ji xu xiang shou zhou ri le
wo zheng zai kan yue han ge li sen mu de xin shu tai bang le ni ye ying gai kan kan
zai ti chu cai zheng shen qing de tong shi
wo men hai neng bao zheng fu zong tong hui fan dui
dui ju liu qi chao guo wu nian de fei fa yi min de huo mian
 xian zai zhe yang cai bi jiao he wo men xin yi
bing qie gong kai biao shi zhi chi ni de li chang
hao le wo hui jia le wo yao hui qu da gan yi chang
zong tong lai guo dian hua ma
ru guo ni neng gou lv xing zhe xie wo hui yong ai wo de sha er zi de re qing
qu zhi chi ge chu rong chang bian lun
er kan zai wo lao po de fen shang
wo kan qi lai xiang shi ai ji le nei ge ke lian de bai chi
hen gao xing ni men zhong yu xue hui le tuo xie
zen mo yang zan men ge rang yi bu
wo jin wan ken ding shui bu zhao le tai hei an le
wo gu ji de hai duo shang le yi ling
yi lai wo jiu de xia yi ling ling ceng
you shi hou wei le shang sheng ni bi xu xian xia jiang
wei zhe ci shi wo gong lao

shi de wo ting dao ta jiang dian hua
cheng shou duo shao ci a
ta de shen ti zhe mo xiao er nei nan ren hao xiang hen da
wei neng bu neng liao dian bie de
wo men neng liao liao wo bu zhi dao
huan de le dui huo zhe bie de shi mo xing ma

e wei da de si wang zhu ming mei guo yao gun le dui

ni you mei you kan jian
wo zai xuan ni shi mu juan hui nei zhang zhao pian xia de biao ti

ta shi ge hun dan

bu ni bu yong nei yao shuo

bu xing geng quan shi tian hou gou pai chu

cong ling kai shi zuo fu mu

o ta o wo de guai guai nv er

mo fang bing bu shi wu fa po jie de
wo jian guo yi ge zhong guo xiao hai yi ling miao zhong jie kai mo fang

rang wo hao hao xiang xiang
ta shuo de mei cuo wo men shi xian ru kun jing le
wo xiang zhe fen gong zuo de xing zhi jiu shi zhe yang o wo ke mei zai bao yuan
wo hen gao xing yuan li chong wu gou he ju feng
hui gui yuan xian yu yue de hua sheng dun bao feng quan
shuo dao gou nei jian fang xian zai shi shi yao qing kuang
jiao gei wo hao de
ni xuan hao gou le yao
ni ma shuo zui zhong jue ding quan zai ni
ta kan shang qu hen zhen liang
hao xiang lian zhao dian lan xian si de
wo jue de ta hen ke ai hao ba shi de shi de

wo shi zhe yao da suan de chu fei

o wo hui li kai
wo neng he ni jian duan di liao liao yao

nei shi tiao shi yao qun zi yi kuai di tan yao

ta zen yao yang le hai hao yao
shi de ta he ping chang mei liang yang
zhen de fei chang hao hen hao
you ji hua zen yao jie kai mo fang le yao
wo yi zhi zai cha kan wo you ge zhu yi
wo men xuan bu ling yang yi tiao gou wen he de chen jian xin wen
dan wo men nong qiao miao dian
shuo wo men xiang wei ta qi ge ming

tong shi wei wo men ying de chu li qi ta po shi de shi jian
zhe suan shi ge hao zhu yi
hao de ta xuan le yi tiao gou yao
ni ta ma de kai wan xiao ni
wo hen si zhe xie dong wu
zhe ge dong xi zhen shi meng dao jia le
nv shi can yi yuan lai le
biao qing jiu xiang shi bei bao ju le
hao ba wo xian zai mei shi jian jian ta yin wei xian zai wo he nv er zai yi qi
ye xu shang wu ding ping tai wu ding ping tai
fu zong tong nv shi ni jiu shi gua fu qi zi zhan zai wu ding ping tai wang fu gui jia cheng huo gua fu
gen wo lai bao bei ni wei shi yao wu shi wo nv shi
wo men jia zhuang bao bei bie zhuan tou
wo yi jing lai le ba tou xiang wo kao long
jiu jia zhuang ni he wo zai tan zheng shi
deng deng ma ma ni de lian zen yao le mei shi yao bao bei
wo shi jia zhuang zai he ni shuo hua dan wo men shi zai shuo hua
bu bu wo shi shuo zhe shi jia zhuang
fu ren ni xiang wo bao zheng guo
gong zuo xiao zu li mei you shi you bei jing de ren
er xian zai zhe ge jiao de zai hu shuo ba dao
zhe zheng jian shi tai wei miao le
wo yao xie diao wu shu fang de li yi
er ling nian qian ni mei quan li dan shi ni you dan liang
xian zai kan kan ni shi de kan kan wo
wo chang le lao er he gao wan hao yao dan liang he gao wan shuang guan
wo men ke bu ke yi bie
bu bie yin wei wo er da duan
zhe zhen de hen you qu
hai wo xiang wo men mei jian guo
dan wo hen gao xing ni zai zhe
gong xi zai hua sheng dun er ling nian le fu zong tong fu ren
fu zong tong jue ding shou yang yi zhi bei jie jiu de dong wu
shi yao dong wu shi yi tiao gou
yi tiao gou zen yao xiang ni de gou yi yang yao

ke bu jin jin shi chui gao yin

ta lao shi ku wo jiu lao shi ying
xian zai wo bei ni rao yun le ting zhao
wo men de shang liang yi xia zhe ge
wan ku qi da fa
wo men zhi xu yao she ji ta yi xia ran hou rang she xiang ji zhuan qi lai
ran hou wo men jiu tong ta de lei dian
wo men zen yao shi shi
ke yi zhao ta pen hu jiao pen wu
shuo ta pang kai wan xiao de
shi yao ba ta nong ku de
que xi mu qin de ci tong
nv er de zhe mo zhe ge hen bu
tian na wo bu xiang xin wo men zai zuo zhe ge le
ling yi fang mian lai shuo wo men xian zai shi zai
hua le yan jing de niu rou pang bian mi mou suo yi
hao le nv shi you dan pao pao you duo hao ma shi de
qia pu qi nuo zheng zhi hao ma e hai e de san da chan ye shi
xiang xiao shi hua nong ye dui de hao
shi jing shuo xiang xiao zhe shi ge da xiang xiao zhou hao de mei wen ti
nei shi shi yao chuan zhen jian yao hai shi ni yi jiu ba ba nian xie gei zi ji de liu yan
ni kan shi shui zai he zong tong da gao er fu
nei shi shi yao bie dan xin
deng yi xia ni jin guan wen ta nv er de shi hao ma
yin wei wo men xi wang ni wen zhi chi lv de wen ti
kan ba ta dui wo zhe yao shuo hua de shi hou wo jiu jue de hen jin zhang
wo men gang zhi dao zhou chang zai he zong tong da gao er fu
suo yi ru guo ni xiang ti zhe ge hua tou de hua hao de
neng hui e hai e zhou lai zhen bang
zui jin zhe ji ge yue ni hen bu shun ba
ni de zu nao gai ge ting zhi bu qian
lv se chan ye chang yi ye si le
ni shuo le hen duo xi wang dai lai gai bian de hua
ni hai jue de zi ji ke yi gai bian shi yao ma
dang ran le shi de wo wei wo men gan dao fei chang zi hao
dui yu mu qian de cheng jiu
gan jue zi ji shi zhong hui you xi le yao
e zhe dui wo lai shuo ke bu shi you xi
er qie liu yan ken ding ye rang ni hen shou shang
dao di ta hui xia tai yao wo cai zhi dao
jin tian zong tong he zhou chang da gao er fu le
zhe ge xiao xi kun rao dao ni le ma
xiang he shui da gao er fu du xing
ke wo lai zhe li shi yin wei wo you gong zuo yao zuo
zhe shi quan nian wu xiu de zhe shi wo de zheng zhi zhi ze
quan nian wu xiu nei jiu shi shuo mei you duo shao shi jian liu gei ni de jia ren le
e zhe shi yi ge rang ren jing pi li jin de ri cheng que shi shi zhe yang
wo shi shuo ni hui ni hui lei
er qie hui bei bei da ji
ni neng xiang xiang ma
ru guo wo lei le de hua
xiang xiang yi xia e hai e zhou de xiang xiao gong ren you duo lei ba
ta tai niu bi le
ri fu yi ri de zhi zuo xiang xiao
wo jue de e hai e jiu shi xiang xiao qiu zhi zhou
ru guo ni zi xi xiang xiang de hua ta yong yuan du hui fan dan hui lai
e hai e gong min min zhu dang chou kuan hui
wo bu zhi dao ta dao di zai xiang shi yao
ni shang yi ci yi tian ku liang hui shi shi yao shi hou
bi ni xiang de yao jin duo le
ling ling qi zhong de yi ge fan pai
guo lai ni lao ban ta ma shi gao shi yao
wo kan jian ta beng kui le
zhong yi yuan wo kan dao de shi re qing he xin nian
wo kan dao de shi ta ma feng po zi
ru guo ta ti dao wo ming zi de hua ru guo wo de dao le zhi chi de hua
yao shi ta dian shi cheng shi de shou gan dong wo yi xia wo jiu chong zhao ni lai peng you
mei li jian guo hui hui nong si ni
qu wen wen ni de peng you ye xu ta neng bang zhu ni
you qing fu zong tong
ni hao shi de wo kan jian ni le
kan kan zhe xie ren a
ta men neng zai wo zhi hou huo dao tou piao de nei tian yao
ha luo a bu neng tou piao de wa wa men
fang tan de hui kui hen hao
ni ye shou dao le ma bu geng hao
wo zai zhe fang jian li yi jing diao cha guo le hen re qing hen you hao
ru guo zhe zai e hai e guan yong nei quan guo du hui mai zhang de
wo zuo le yi ge dan gao shang mian you ni de lian
nei kan qi lai jiu xiang shi wo zai can yi yuan du guo le man chang yi tian de yang zi
ta jiu juan le wu ling
fu zong tong nv shi shi yao
wo yao gei ni jie shao yi wei zhen zheng de bai jin juan zeng zhe
wo you yi xie guan yu shui gai de xiang fa xiang he ni liao liao
wo hen xiang ting e zhe shi shang you liang zhong ren
a ha dui ba you yi zhong shi zhua qu zhe
ran hou shi ling yi zhong
wo mei you gei ta men qu ming zi ta men bu zhua dong xi
zhua qu zhe hao ba
ta men zhua zhu shi jie de dan dan hao ma
er ta men rang shi jian fa sheng zhe ge kou wei tai zhong le
o dui bu qi dui bu qi shi yao
wo bu zhi dao yao shuo shi yao suo yi wo jiu zhi hao dui ni er yu le
zhong dong de wen ti ni yi hui er zai shuo ba
wo men hai you yi wan shang ni hen gan ji ni hao
wo zhi shi xiang li
zhe bang er huo yuan yuan de
zhao ge an jing de jiao luo zi ji chi dong xi hao ma
zhe jiu shi zhua qu zhe de jing sui
ni yi wei jiu ping wo she zai qiang shang de zhe xie qian
wo chi de hui bi jia xin ji xiong rou qiang
jiu shi wo gao su ni ba zhe xie cheng bao huo shi de a
wo juan le san wan kuai jiu huan le yi kuai ji xiong rou
nei ge ren lian wu ling ling kuai ye mei juan ta ye de le yi kuai ji xiong rou
nei wo de de shi shi yao xian liao yao  heng
hao ba gei wo lai ge ji tui shi yao de a
zhen gao xing jian dao ni wei sha ni re shang guan si le
hao ba ting zhao shi zhe yao hui shi er
wo ke neng re shang le dian er ma fan
yao shi wo bei guo hui wei yuan hui zhi xun le zen yao ban
zhe yang de hua ni xu yao zhun bei san ge shuo ci
lei si wo zi ji de ban ben dui fang de ban ben hai you zhen shi ban ben shi ba
shu mian de kou tou de he yi fen jian duan de kou tou ban ben
you de shi hou hui you shi jian xian zhi hao ba
guo hui wei yuan hui wen wen ti ni dang ran de shuo zhen hua
chu dian er shi yao cha cuo ni jiu hui yin zuo wei zheng bei qi su
bie gei zi ji re ma fan ting jian mei
jiu di diao dian er xiao xin xing shi
hao ba nei ru guo zhen de fa sheng le
wo bei jiao qu zhi xun nei shi ge shi yao qing kuang a
ni xiang xiang yi xia zuo meng meng jian gan lan qiu dui jiao lian chong ni fa biao
ni jiu di zhao tou hai chuan de gen xiu lan deng bo er si de jie xia lai jiu bei da de jiu man di zhao ya le xiang xiang de chu bu
zhe ge gen guo hui wei yuan hui bi qi lai jian zhi shi meng huan di shi ni
ni hui jing li ge lei wen ti ke neng shi wen he de ye ke neng shi yan li de kao wen
shen zhi zao dao dang pai gong ji yin wei you ren yi ding hui hua zhong qu chong
ran hou yi dan ta men chang dao le tian tou ta men jiu hui jue de ni bu xing le
ran hou da si gong ji
ni gao bu hao hai hui bei bian shi
lao tian ye a bian shi
jiu shi jiu suan ni yi jing dao le ta men hai hui die die bu xiu di gong ji ni
bing qie le zai qi zhong
yin wei ren ren du xiang shang dian shi dong bu
ta men hui yi zhi tan lun ni
zhong xin gan xie da jia ge wei wan shang hao
xian sheng zhe ge liu lei xi ma da jia hen mai zhang a
ai ya ma a mei cuo
ta shi yi wei ni men du shi fen shu xi de ren
kuai guo lai fang song dian er xing bu
wo gen ta tan guo le ni men ye tan guo le
ta bu ke neng bei shu zhi chi ni de
bu bu bu ta bi xu xian zai jiu bei shu
ting dong mei ta yi jing cong ren ren xian bian cheng ren ren ai le
fan zheng jiu deng wo men yi dian tou ni jiu gen ta fang hua ting dong mei
ni lia xian zai gao de wo wei zhuo re le du
wo hua le yi xia wu shi jian an zhao ni lia yi si lai
jie guo xian zai ke you bu wan er le ni tou yi hui yu dao yao
wo kan ta hao xiang kuai shuo wan le
hao ba ni gan jue ru he
zhe yang a wo shi ge zheng zhi shang de ma feng bing ren qing gan shang de ding shi zha dan
suo yi ni cai zen yao zhao zan shang tai ba
nv shi men xian sheng men xie xie ge wei
tai mei miao le xie xie ge wei
qing ru zuo xie xie ge wei zhe shi wo
kuai dian er ni deng sha ni kuai dian er gei xin hao

ni ta ma dong dian er nao zi a shu ge da mu zhi sha de
wo de tian a jin tian zhen shi
fei bi xun chang bu shi ma
ta ke bu neng yi tian ku san hui
ta de lei xian you duo fa da a
ma chao xi si de yi zhen yi zhen de
zai zhe yang kai xin de chang he
lao tian ye a wo qu bie bei shu le
wo fei chang rong xing neng lai dao lian bang di yi qi ge zhou
wo de zu fu lai zi xin xin nei ti
wo jia guo qu chang shuo zhe yao yi ju hua
wo men chang shuo bu xi huan zi ji de
dan shi lai zi e hai e zhou wo zi hao
hao le bei shu kuai bei shu
ni que ding bei shu kuai dian er
reng ran xiang nian wo de zu fu
gan ma ni da li shui shou

ni kan zhi jia ge xian qu lun tan bao mei

hao a zhe ke bu shi zan mei
ta ren wei cui ruo shi ren xing de ruo dian
wo xi huan ni ma shuo de ke shi wo ma a
zao ni kan zhi jia ge xian qu lun tan bao mei
kan jian le kan guo le xiao hua le
wo mu yu zai cheng gong de fen wei li ru jin wo hui lai la gu niang xiao huo er men
shi a gen xiang xiao shang di si de

shuo zhen de rang wo zhi chi
da jia hai bu zhang sheng gu li yi xia
kuai dian er a da jia gu zhang
dao zhe xie ren li mei yi ge zhen xin xi huan ni de
shui hui zai hu a
da jia hao ai ya zhe yao long zhong
shi ya ye shi shi hou le xie xie
zong tong xian sheng dui shi tai de xin fa zhan hen man yi
wo she fa rang zai dian shi shang ku chu lai le
wo jiu shi mu ou da shi pi nuo cao

e dui wu sui wa wa du zhi dao
nan shi ju le bu you sha zhi shi
wo shi lai biao da zong tong de zhi chi de
xian sheng da dian hua
zhe yang de bu shi zhen zheng yi yi shang de dian hua
shi rang wo lai chuan da yi ge dian hua de yi si 
ta gen wo wo you yi ge zhong da xiao xi yao xuan bu
qing da jia gen wo jin ban gong shi
zhe bian qing  wo shi xiang
jin xing yi xiang gai zu
tai xie xie ni le bu yong ke qi
wo gang qian le fen zu che he tong ru guo wo neng zai duo dai ban nian
yi hou wo mei tian de dui wai fan bo du you ni lai fu ze hao ma
zheng ce he gong gong yan jiang fang mian yi hou you ni fu ze
xie xie ni zhe jiu shi wo bi sheng suo qiu a
wo bi sheng bu xie
ta xian zai cheng wo shang si le
wo neng ping lun yi ju bu zhe tai jing cai le
wo xiang wo you huo er yao gan le
sha huo er a ni bu xu yao zhi dao
zhe zhong xin xi bu dui ni kai fang
zhen hao xiao zhen de jia de
zhen ke bei ni jiu gen

hai neng ge jia guan shang ni gun dan
wo cai wo an quan ba
ni wei le wo jia zhuang liu chan
ni reng ran shi wo dui wu zhong bu ke huo que de yi yuan
ting hao le gu niang xiao huo er wo sheng zhi le

nei rong wo yi jing xie hao le
gei ni ge ji hui
zai wo de wen jian jia di yi duan li
ban zhe zhang zhuo zi
dong zuo kuai bie gei wo bai yi zhang ku bi gu er lian
ba ni de ling shi dai zi he ni de shui ping zi dai hao gan jin gun chu lai
gong xi sheng zhi le zan lia you kong he yi bei qu
ni cai zen yao de gen wo mi shu shuo yi sheng
bu xing bu xing ni de ban hui qu
wo ke bu zhun ni ding zhao wo yi zheng tian
bu zhun ta ban dao nei er qu fang song dian er niu yan wa
wo cai bu hui zuo zai zhe er
yi zhi ding zhao ni de niu yan kan ni deng zi fang zhe er

ta men rang wo xiang ban fa bi ta ku chu lai

rang ni ku chu lai de
ta shuo ta shi ni de mu ou da shi
ta shuo ta shi ni de pi nuo cao

bi sa xie ta bu shi

wei de shi yan gai
wo men qiang po qun zhong can yu mu juan hui zhe ge shi shi
xian zai wo bu xiang bei ni zhe xie huang yan qian lian
er qie shuo ju shi zai de wo ke bu yuan yi tang ni zhe hun shui
shou xian yi yuan xian sheng
wo yi jing shou gou ni zhe xie pi hua le
qi ci di yi tiao zai ci qiang diao yi bian
ku shi yan chu lai de wo shi bei cao zong de
zhe ge hui yi ye gai jie zhi le
yin wei zhe ya gen er jiu bu ying gai bei ti shang ri cheng
yao bu wo bu ke qi le
ni gan ma yong nei ku le si wo
ni bao li you kou qi qing xin ji mei zou ba
ni mei xin you ge hong dian a
ni bei miao shang le wo gao su ni ni shuo sha
ni zui hao zhuang bei qi lai niu zi yin wei wo yao dui zhe jian ban gong shi
zhan kai guo hui diao cha ting zheng
xiang mu shi xiu zheng an he zong rong xia shu fu
wo jue de ni ying gai qu zheng yi ge tou kui
zai jia shang ge fang dan bei xin he xia ti tie hu shen
yin wei wo hui zhao ren bao ni tou tong ni bei rang ni dan sui
ni zan shi bie sheng zhi le
hao yao bao chi di diao
wo mao si yi jing fa le yi tiao xin wen gao
guan yu wo sheng zhi de zhen de jia de
nei wo neng ba ni che le bu kong pa bu xing
cheng le wo shang si le
tou xian shang shi dan ni bi ta zi shen

da xie zi mu de

hou tian ye bu xing
na tian du bu xing
min zhu shi ge hao dong xi
bu guo zhe wan yi ye tai chun le ba
ta men yi dian yao fen sheng fu de yi si du mei you
gen ben jiu bu yong lai

bu ta bu neng zai dian shi zhi bo de shi hou shui zhao
a zheng lun zhi bo tai zhe yang feng ci xing tai gao
ni zhe shi zai hui shou yao ta ke bu neng wang chuan dian shi kan dao ni e
yi ban ren si sui zuo you jiu ming bai zhe ge dao li le
wo men ke yi da dian hua gei ta zhen dong hui zhen xing ta de

bu shi de mei you
mei you zhi shi nei li hen nuan he er yi
wa tou dun le yi xia gang cai ta dun le yi xia hao la
ni que ding ding de shi jin tian zao shang ba dian yao
hao ba wo cuo le ni dang ran que ding la
bi xu de qing bu yao zhe yang ding zhao wo le
yong yan shen bo guang wo de gan jue wo shi yong yan shen gei ni duo chuan dian
lv se chan ye de huo jian yi jing cha bu duo dao shi hou sheng kong le dui ba
sui ran xi jie shang hai xu yao yi xie da mo bu guo shi de

hao de nei ni chuan hao yu hang fu ba
shuo dao yu hang fu

ni zhi dao ta men yu hang yuan zui pa shi yao ma
zai er si xiao shi zhi nei lian kan yi qi bian ri chu hao ba

wo jin tian shi shi yao ri cheng
ni xia wu yao qu can jia yi ge she qu da xue jian mian hui
zhe jiu mei le shi de
bu bu bu zhe yang bu dui
hao ba deng yi fen zhong ru guo ni wang xia gun ping ni
nei yao shi wang shang gun ni nei yi jing guo qu le nv shi

qu na le wo zhao le ta yi zao shang le
gei wo liu le yu yin you xiang hu han ta de ming zi
jiu shi wo men ping chang gan de nei yang
wo jue de ba zan men ying gai kai chang jiang ge xiao hua

hao ba mei guan xi

 hao ba mei guan xi

er zheng ke men du

ni men shi qu yi ge shi yao di fang lai zhao

yao ba shi tan zi pu dao shi yao dong xi shang
ni chi dao le shi de er qie wo fei chang fei chang bao qian
wo zuo wan bu shi zai jia shui de wo jiu shi shui guo tou le
hao ba chi dao zhi hou shuo ni zhong feng shi yao de hai xing
shuo ni xing fu le shi jue dui bu xing de
shuo de dui nv shi dan shi ba
wo hai yi wei ni bu zai ban gong shi wei shi yao
e zai bai gong you yi chang guan yu cai zheng ze ren ti an de jian bao
wo yi wei ni hui zai nei bian
ta men mei you yao qing wo shi yao
zhe ge shi yao jiu xian zai
qu ta niang de zong tong
ta liang zhou qian guo fang yu suan jian bao de shi hou jiu mei you yao qing wo
ni dai zhao yi ge du zui de
wei shi yao wo bu zhi dao zhe jian shi
wo yi ding yao qu ta men bu neng ba wo liang zai wai mian
nv shi wo zai zhe li ni ni xu yao shi yao dong xi ma
ni you han bing xie ma
cai zheng ze ren zhe tai che le
ni wan wo ni ba zhe xie ren
du shi nian mei zi ji chu guo wu fan qian le ba feng ci ge zhong gong zuo can
wo jue de wo chu xi le jiu hen biao ming tai du
fei chang a bu guo wo chuan qi sheng you dian da
bu hui you ren zhu yi de ba
hai you fei qi zhong ni
ting qi lai gen gu feng ji yi ge xiao guo
zhe ge que shi shi ta gei ren de shen qi yin xiang
fu zong tong nv shi zen yao le
ni shi lai zhao wo men de ma o bu shi de
wo de qing yi ge xiao shi shi jia
wo he ying yang shi you yu yue
o ni mei shi ba hui hao qi lai de
wo shi guo tang bu nai shou
guo tang jiu shi shui guo li de tang fen
zhe hen han jian o
nei zhu ni hao yun ba
ni hai yi wei ta yi jing guai dao zui dian feng le
ya jiu guai shang yi ceng lou gei ni kan tian na
zhi qian de shi hen bao qian wo yi wei ni hai zai wei zi shang ni
hao ba wo xian zai yao quan ti kai hui
hao de ni zhi dao ma wo xu yao he mei ge ren kai ge hui yi
wo yao yi bei ka fei
xian zai de wen ti shi
zong tong zai duo wo
shuo bu ding ta jiu shi fan bing ni jiu gen de jiao yi yang
bu shi de wo le jie ta ta hen tao yan zheng mian chong tu
xian ran xian zai jiu shi ta you shi yao yao he wo chong tu de shi le
nei ta hai hui ming que di zhi chi wo de lv se chan ye ti an yao
zhe shang mian wo xu yao bai gong de ke kao xiao xi
hao de bai jian dui
wo lai gao ding hen hao
hao de qu ba qu ba hao de hao de
wo yao kan kan jin wan xiao fang xie hui de zhe ge shi
du you na bao dao le
wa ni zhe shi yao zi sou yao shi de
wo men ban gong shi li you ren fu ze zhe ge de a nv shi
huan wo de hua jiu bu hui sou suo ni de ming zi chuo hao shi yao de
wo de chuo hao wo de chuo hao shi shi yao
jiu shi yi xie wo men qu sou bo ke de shi hou
yong dao de xiao ai cheng er yi
dan shi wo de yi si shi du you shi yao chuo hao e hao ba

zai gong gong chang he mu ru wei yang
nei shi ge hao fa an a nei que shi shi ge hao fa an
ru xian bu shi ba
jiu xiang zhe ge yi yang hai you bie de
o bu shi ba hao ba
xia fu ren xi rui gong zhu huang xi rui wei mou gu lao qia tong ren wu
bian fu wo niao niao lian bian fu xia de ji di
xi yi nv wu duo zui fu zong tong xi yi wei bai gong ban gong qu suo zai di
fu te jia mei niao fan dai ke wei zhu ming xi ju yan yuan
can yan he ben jin fa nv wu yong
bu bu shi zhe ge biao qing
hua ping shi bei di
ren men shi yin wei ni mei mao yu zhi hui bing zhong er gong ji ni de
ni hen duo chuo hao du shi dang chu shang feng mian de shi hou jiao chu lai de
zhe ge wo ji de ta men jiu shi xian mu ji du hen ji de ma
ta men shuo ni xiao de ju sha zhe ge jiu bie shuo le
wan le kan qi lai ni nv peng you
mei you dang shang yi chang de mu liao chang a
nei wo jiu bu yong mai mao zi le
mao zi shi hun li ma
wo zai shen shang hua le hen duo shi jian
wo jin tian gu yi chi dao jiu shi yao ta xiang xin
ta bi gong zuo dui wo geng zhong yao
wo hen huai yi bu guo zhe zhong xiang fa shi hen zhong yao de
ta hen xin shang wo zuo chu le pian ta de zi tai
ke xi wo men zhi jian de hao shi guang hu ran jiu jie shu le
da gai ba fen zhong zhi qian de yang zi nei xia yi wei shi shui
shui jia you li yong jia zhi de mei zi
hui jian zheng ni liang xiao shi de qing chen hu fu liu cheng ni
ni xi huan zhe li ma wo ai si zhe li le
shi de du shi gan huo
zhe li du shi huo zhen jia shi de ha
deng yi hui ta men ba mian bao na chu lai de shi hou ni zi xi kan
nei ke shi hua li li de yi da tuo a xiang xin wo du gou yi jia ren chi le
yi jia da pang zi chi nei yao duo mian bao du gou le
wo yao lai yi bei cheng zhi ni yao ma
bu yao a mei men ge men you guo tang
wo shuo lv se chan ye de shi hen bu cuo ha
nei bai gong zen yao shuo ni ta men he wo men yi yang xing fen ma
ge men wo du chu le ban gong shi le
wo bu xiang shuo gong shi ha o hao ba hao ba
chong kou er chu ha wo men zhe jiu shi dan chun de liang ge ren zai yi qi
shi shi de wo xi huan he ni yi qi
xie le ge men hao de
xi bu xi huan he ni zai yi qi
ke suan le ba ta jiu shi xian mu ji du hen er yi
ni men lia yue hui guo zhi hou ni jiu xing dong le dui ba
o feng kuang de xing dong a
wo de lao er jiu gen qia pu qi nuo qi pao qi yi yang
da de nei zhong e dian li mian yong de nei zhong bu shi xiao de
kan wo shuo de ba zhe jiu shi ta ma de liang ge gu cang a
shi a zhe jiu shi zheng chang de liang shi qun huo dong
dui le ni you mei you ting zai nei xia lie lie
shuo zong tong zai duo zhao lai zhao
pi du bu zhi dao
ta de zhi nang jiu zhi you ta zi ji de dian nao er yi

hao xiao hua zong tong zhi dao lv se chan ye de shi you xi
can yi yuan ken ding hui fu yi zhe ge ti an de
ta wei le zhe ge hen xing fen
wo qu ta men yao wo xian zai hui xi yi
shi yao ta men yao dui shui xuan zhan ma bu shi shi qing geng zao gao
guan wang de hu dong can guan qu gua le
jin wan zai you ji duan jin shu le dui biao yan
jiu wan quan shi zao yin de nei zhong le dui lian ming zi du mei you
ni xiang qu ting ma shi a ge men
wo men lai zheng dian da sheng de ting ba ge xie ye li liu tang de quan shi jin shu
tai hao le ni xiang yao dian shi yao
wo xiang yao qu bie jia can ting chi fan
nei de xiao hua du mei yong ma
shi de xiao fang yuan men shi xi guan kan jian you ren chui si
dan bu shi nei zhong si fa
ting zhao wo men bi xu gong xi
zhe ge lv se chan ye ti an de cao an tai bang le
shi a gai you de ji ben shang du you le wo men zhi yao
ti gao shi zhi xing de chu fa yao guan yu wei gui chu fa
ni bu jue de chu fa ying gai geng zhong yi xie yao
wo jue de wo men jiu ying gai zhe yao ban
wo jue de wo ying gai fa si zhe bang hun dan
zhi dao zhe bang hun dan bei fa hao wei zhi fa he hao du shi
nei ye tai bu xiang hua le ba
bu xiang hua bu xiang hua
shun bian shuo yi xia zhe yi jing bu shi di yi ci le
ta bu ying gai biao lu gan qing de
ta jiu ying gai xiang ge ji qi yi ji yi yang
wo hui chu li de hao de
ke wo men hai shi bu zhi dao fa an
shi bu shi hui de dao zong tong de ming que zhi chi
zheng zai nu li qu de xiao xi
wo yao wo yao hui jia le
ru guo ke yi de hua ru guo bu xu yao wo le de hua shi hao
bao li shi shi yao
wo jin wan yao shang di yi tang wu ke yi zhong you yang jian shen wu
zhen hao wo hen xing fen
wo xiang he wo yao gong zuo dao hen wan
ni neng bang wo ge mang ma
cong qu yi xia xie bing yao
wo ai si xie bing le shi a
zhe yang hui da luan ni de ji hua ma bu hui nv shi
hei hai you bie de shi yao chuo hao
bu yao a ni zhe shi shou nve kuang le
bu shi de wo lian pi hen hou
wo zhi shi gan xing qu er yi
zhi shi ge zhong suo xie er yi
jiu shi ba he da tou de ci lian qi lai gao xiao
bi fang shuo ni xu niang ban lao
wei ge jin yong zhe tou ming xiao nei nei
wei ge jin yong zhe
wei shi yao yin wei nan ren kan le wo du bu xu yao yong wei ge yao
yi si shi jiu suan yi ge nan de chi le yao
ta men shi shuo zhe zhong li lun shang lai shuo
bu guan nan ren nian ling he jian kang zhuang kuang
du ke yi bao zheng qiang er chi jiu bo qi de chu fang yao
jiu yin wei wo shi xiao le ma
ni men zai ye bu xu sou wo de chuo hao le
ni gang shuo ni lian pi hen hou de
nei ke shi gong wei a ni zhi dao shi shi yao yi si ma
wo ai pao de fu zong tong
shi lai yi pao de hao ba
a zhe zhen ta ma yuan sheng tai a
ni zhi dao ma ni zai shang du zhao bu dao zhe bang ren
ni zhi dao wei shi yao ma yin wei ta men mei you ming zi ma
yin wei ta men du ta ma shi fei mai pin
ni ta ma hao hao ting ting
zhe jiu ta ma de xiang shi hua li shu
zai na ju zi ju dong xi si de tai xian feng le
dui zhe jiu shi wo dui lv se chan ye fa an de gan jue
zong tong shuo mei shuo zhe ge yi cheng neng zou duo yuan
suo you de yi jian du hen hao wo ming tian qu kai hui
ken ding hui tao lun zhe ge shi de wo hui gei ni da dian hua de

ni xian qu mai zhe yi lun jiu xia yi lun wo lai hai you na dian hua sheng lai
wo ba suo you de kuang wu zhi du chu han chu dao duan ku li qu le
ji de gao dian hua sheng
ni zhi dao ma wo rang he ban yan le fan dui ti an de e mo
mo ni le yi xie zheng yi
jiu shi ren men fan dui ti an de shi hou shuo de nei xie hua
ta yi jing shi e mo dai yan ren le

 heng cheng xing le

bu lv se chan ye qia zai qi zhong
wo de lv se chan ye mei cuo

zhi qian zen yao yi dian xiao xi du mei you
bo ke shang xian qian que shi you xie dong zuo

bu shuo hua shi ba
ni nan peng you zhi dao zhe hui shi er yao

zhe jiu gen na yang jiao bao
dang jia yang ju yi yang wo yi wei
sheng sheng ba shuo bai le jiu shi
tou ji bu cheng shi ba mi
wo xu yao dian shi yao hao de shi shi yao te shu de dong xi ma
wo ta ma bu zhi dao wo jiu shi xu yao dian shi yao
ni zhi dao wo da suan zuo shi yao ma

bu kai wan xiao wo yao rang ta shou hui ta de gou pi jue ding
wo jue de ta mei you ren he li you
nv shi wo men xian jing guan qi bian hao ma
xian jing guan qi bian
zhe jiu shi ni de jian yi
yao shi gen ni yi kuai er kun zai zhao huo de lou li wo jiu wan le
wo hen shan chang ying dui huo zai nv shi da rao yi xia
wo you ge zhu yi wo men bu ru qu zhao yi wei you shan de can yi yuan
ti yi you ta jiang lv se chan ye zhong de zhu yao nei rong
wu ran zhi zao zhe zhi cai huan bao qi ye shui fu jian mian
zuo wei cai zheng ze ren fa an de
xiu zheng an tian jia jin qu
zhe yang yi lai jiu xiang dang yu tong guo le lv se chan ye bu shi ma
dan shi zhe hui wu ni zong tong de yi yuan
zhe shi tiao xin nv shi shi a
wo zheng xiang zhao ren tiao xin ni
wo quan shen shang xia du shi tiao xin yin zi
wo fa xian le nv shi
zong tong bu hui gao xing de wo xian zai jiu gan duan yan
zhe shi ge xian jing wo zhi dao ni shuo de dui
wo men bu neng zhe yao zuo shi bu shi wo men bu neng
zhi yao wo men xiang you shi yao bu neng zuo de
ni dang zhe shi pai dian ying ni mei shi qi dao he lian ai
ting wo jie shi wo bu neng
bei zhao zong tong tou tou gan she li fa
tai feng kuang le hui bei shi zuo bei pan
nv shi yi yuan hen xin shang zhe xiang fa an ta hui tong yi wo men de zuo fa
ting zhao ru guo yi yuan zi yuan zhe yao zuo
nei jiu wan shi da ji ming bai ma
dan shi wo bu neng bei ren zhi dao gan zhe shi er
nv shi wo gei nin mai le dian er bing qi lin
wo xiang ni ke neng xu yao zhe ge
neng nong dian er sheng nai you lai yao dang ran gei wo yi fen zhong
wo xiang gao su ni dan shi wo bu neng
bu zhi dao ni ming bai mei
wo zhong yu zong tong
gou pi ni gen ben bu zhi dao ta hui fan kou lv se chan ye
ni pi du bu zhi dao wo zhi dao
ni cai zen yao zhao wo men yi hou bu yao jian mian le
bie zhe yang dui bu qi
ni de yi si shi jiu yin wei wo gen zong tong
mei you ni xiang de nei yao qin jin
wo men jiu bu neng zai yi qi le
wo de yi si shi da xing xing tong zhi
ni ta ma jiu shi ge che tou che wei de fei wu
wo ben lai hai xiang li yong ni yi xia
jie guo ni ta ma lian dian li yong jia zhi de mei you
hai you shang cai shang zhe yao da fen de can ting
jue dui suan bu shang shi yao hao di fang
gang cai de mian bao shi gou chi le a hun dan
ni ni zhe ge niu yue jiao qu de sha bi qiao qiao a
zen yao le lao zi shuo de jiu shi niu yue jiao qu
ni men ta ma de hai dang zi ji shi niu yue ren ni men ya gen er bu shi
qiao qiao ni la li la ta man lian hu chi
wo gen ben bu xiang he ni zai yi qi
shi ma wo dao jue de ni you dian er xi huan wo
suo yi ni cai hui zhe yao sheng qi
ni ta ma jiu shi gen lao er
wan shang shui jue de shi hou dang xin dian er hun dan
mei zhun wo hui dai zhao yi da bao ju zi
liu jin ni de gong yu li chi si ni
wo men gai cong ba li gei zong tong ji zhang ming xin pian
shou hui ni de gou pi jue ding yong fa yu zen yao shuo
shuo shi hua wo you dian er pa ba li nv ren
bu zhi dao ta men you dian er tai ba li le
ni gen ba li nv ren yi yang shi mao
o ni ye shi xie xie
ting dun de you dian er jiu le shi bu shi
wo men qu bu le ba li le cao
bu wo men du an pai hao xing cheng le
ni zen yao you shuo an jing zen yao le
ta men yu gan can yi yuan tou piao jie guo hui shi ping ju
nin you de hui qu zhu chi le
qiao xiao chui de shi ke dao le na xiang fa an
yuan hua shi gai lun qi da lang tou le wo zhi dao wo wen ni shi na xiang fa an
bu shi ba shi xiu zheng an
shi de shi zhi shang jiu shi lv se chan ye
nin da suan tou zhi chi hai shi fan dui
an zhao wo de yuan ze he liang zhi de zhi yin
ni jue de gai zhi chi hai shi fan dui
wo yi jing shuo guo wo de kan fa le
zong tong jue dui bu xi wang
lv se chan ye xiu zheng an tong guo
zai ping ju de qing kuang xia tou zhi chi
ni de zhi chi zi ji de zheng ce shi ma ni zhe yao kan
ni zhen de xi wang wo
hui le zhe xiang zheng ce hui le wo men shu yue
shen zhi shi shu nian de gong zuo cheng guo ma
xiang xiang wo men de nu li
hao ba shuo bai le jiu shi
ni ru ci tao yan zhe xiang zheng ce
bie jie shi que xiang rang wo tou zhi chi piao
er ni ni zan tong zhe xiang zheng ce
que xiang rang wo tou fan dui
zhe nan dao shi shi yao gou pi gui yi de jing zhong shi jie yao
tou fan dui tou zhi chi
nv shi ta men rang ni xia qu
dai hui er jian le tong zhi men
shi ni rang jia shang zhe ze xiu zheng an de shi bu shi
wo jiu zhi dao shi ni zi ji you nao zi
ru guo shi ni gan de
ni jiu shi wei bei le de ming ling
hai jiang zhe zheng jian ban gong shi zhi yu xian jing
ni gan ma ni zai cha qiu sai bi fen
o huo ji ta hui zen yao zuo
an wo shuo de zuo
ben ci tou piao zhi chi piao wu ling fan dui piao wu ling
can yi yuan tou piao jie guo zheng fan can ban
fu zong tong tou fan dui piao
zhe xiang xiu zheng an wei tong guo
wo can zheng jiu shi wei le zuo zhe xie ma
wo jiu shi xiang zheng xing di wen wen
xian ran wo can zheng bu shi wei le zhe ge

ni de gun hui dao lao ban jiao xia qu le
ye zhong qiang le you bo ke bao liao cheng
yi gu can yi yuan he ta you guo yi duan bu lun xing shi
zhi dao ma wo bu wei can yi yuan gong zuo le
wo yi ge xiao shi qian ci zhi de
wo xie mi le nei ge gu shi yi
ni neng ding zhao ta ma
hao de wo men zhe yao zuo
yi yi dian ban de shi hou ni shuo can yi yuan
bu jin wu ru le yi gu can yi yuan
er qie ta shan dong
bu deng deng yao jia zhong yu qi ta gu li
fu zong tong zai xiao hua zhong yong tuo ta zhe ge ci
zhi dao wo zai zuo shi yao le ma can yi yuan
yao wei tuo ta men fu ze
ni shi nei zhong gu zuo cong ming de ren ma
yin wei kan qi lai xiang
hao hao kan kan wo
wen wen ni zi ji
ni yan qian de zhe ge ren
zai wei lai de yi nian nei hui
dang ni de lao ban hai shi shou xia
hen duo nian qian ni you de shi chou chu man zhi
zai wei lai yi ling nian de gong zuo sheng ya zhong ni suo you de zhi shi
chao shi de gong yu bing leng de xie bing
hai you yi zhi yin xing de gou
ni dao di xiang bu xiang zhao zhe ge ji hua zhi xing
hao hao suan suan ge men
ni huo de gong ke xue shi xue wei de shi hou mei xue guo zen yao xie xin wen bao dao ma
wo xiang wo ting shuo guo
ta na zhao wei wen qia zou le ma
wo xiang wo qian le wo de ming zi
de ming zi wo de ming
hao ba hao ba deng deng
cong yi dao yi ling de ken ding cheng du yi ci zeng jia ni you duo ken ding
wo zhi dao zhe fan wei shi yao yi si
cha bu duo shi yi ling
wo qian le wo ming
ru guo wo zai xie hui yi lu qi shi mei xie
dan ru guo wo xie zhe ke shi ge da shi ke
bu neng rang ren zhi dao
bu neng rang ta zhi dao
bu bu ni zai zuo shi yao
zhen de hen bao qian wo yao he ni shuo dian shi
wo zai li mian xiang ba liang ba huo mie le
ran hou zhuan guo tou fa xian
ni ba xiao fang che dian zhao le
bao qian bao qian bao qian
zhe ge ban gong shi li ren yuan de bu cheng zhi cheng du jian zhi dao le tian li bu rong de di bu
wo men hui ba qia na hui lai
ba zhe ge gao ding hao ma
yin wei wo mang zhao gen dao mei de tuo ta
xian sheng wo hen bao qian
jin tian zhen shi zhuang kuang bai chu
wo bu tai xiang kai zhe ge xin wen fa bu hui
dang ran nin de xing fu yu fou shi wo de shou yao ren wu
yuan yuan gao yu qi hou wen ti he mai mai er tong
tian a hui bu hui fa zhan cheng gou xie qing jie
wo men zhui ru ai he ran hou kai shi luan gao
yao qu de ban gong shi
ran hou shen bu zhi gui bu jue di ba qia na hui lai
wo mei chuan da yi wo de ba qia cang qi lai
ni ke yi jie wo de da yi
xie xie ni zhen hao
shou xian ni yao ba mao zi zhai le
wo mei da suan ba mao zi
wo xiang xin ni hai shi neng gan hao de
yong wo tong zhi ta men ni yao lai ma
dian ran le xian chang de qing xu
ni shi lai tou nei zhang cuo qian de qia ma
wo jue de ni bu shi
fang song hao ma wo hui ba qia gei ni
hao ma shuo shi hua wo you dian hai pa
shuo ba yin wei wo zhi dao ni you tiao jian
wo bu xi huan zhe zhong jin zhang qi fen
wo xiang jin wan he yue hui
hao ba hao ba hao ba zhe bu ke neng
bie dan xin hao ma wo men bu
ru guo suo you wo xiang yu zhi fa sheng guan xi de ba fen
zhi dao wo neng ba dao yi ge ba fen
nei wo hen kuai jiu neng he yi ge ba
zhe shi shi xi ji
ni kan wo xiang la pi tiao de ma
ni kan qi lai jiu shi ge la pi tiao de
deng zhao diao xian bing ni
wo de he ta tan yi xia

wa ni gan de hao

wo qu gei hei mei chong dian
ni gu le hua sheng dun tou hao hun dan

shi wo de zhao pai zhi yi
wo li yong de dao wo xiang yao de dong xi
ta li yong ni de dao ta xiang yao de
bu wo ken ding shi li yong ta
wo shi li yong zhe ta shi bei yong zhe
xia ren yi mian zai lai yi ge pian
shi ji rou yi mian wo
shi ge yin mou jia ta hen jiao hua
wo zhi dao suo yi wo cai hui gu ta ni wei shi yao bu ting wo de
ban nian nei suo you zhe xie lan shi xiao ting le
wo men wang qing ji gong zuo wei yuan hui li an cha yi ge shi you de ren
ni yao wang qing ji gong
tian a cheng shu dian ba
ta men jiu shi zhe yang jie jue gu ba dao dan wen ti de

gao su ni zhe shi ni de gu ba ma
ta zhen shi tuo shi

ni jiu shi ba ta dang tuo shi mai gei wo de suo yi wo gu le ta

su liao he xian wei su hua he wu xie hui de
ni zhi dao wo you zi ji de qi ma

ni de zhan che zai deng
